(338, '', 'Bakery ', 'Beverages', 'Fruit Juices & Drinks', 'Real', 'Fruit Power Juice - Mosambi', 'Juices', 'NA', 'Sweet Lime is also known as Mosambi is a versatile fruit with a sweet and sour taste. Packed with 20 fruits, Real Mosambi is a refreshing source of Vitamin C and potassium! This healthy and refreshing drink is a perfect addition to your breakfast. Made from the best quality fruits, Réal does not have artificial flavours and preservatives, and offer your kids not just great taste, but also Fruit Power - the power of fruits… the power to stay ahead.', '1', 'Ltr', '1', '110.00', '96.800', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40083959_7-real-fruit-power-juice-mosambi.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
