(341, '', 'Bakery ', 'Beverages', 'Fruit Juices & Drinks', 'Real', 'Fruit Power Juice - Pomegranate', 'Juices', 'NA', 'Pomegranate, the super nutritious fruit, is well recognized in various leading world cultures. The super fruit, as well as the juice of Pomegranate, is known to deliver health in every meal. We at Réal ensure that you get the best quality of a pomegranate beverage by providing the goodness of 8 pomegranates in each pack. Real Fruit Power ensures that you sip the healthiest pomegranate fruit beverage in the market which contains all the benefits of pomegranate juice.', '1', 'Ltr', '1', '115.00', '97.750', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/265853_9-real-fruit-power-juice-pomegranate.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
