(355, '', 'Bakery ', 'Beverages', 'Fruit Juices & Drinks', 'B Natural', 'Juice - Guava Gush', 'Juices', 'NA', 'Enjoy the thick and pulpy goodness of Guava with this delicious beverage of B Natural. Made directly from the best of fruits and Not from Concentrate, this beverage assures the nutritive goodness of anti-oxidants and Vitamin C and an authentic experience of the fruit goodness with no preservatives, artificial colours or flavours.', '1', 'Ltr', '1', '110.00', '64.350', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/100076751_10-b-natural-juice-guava-gush.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(356, '', 'Bakery ', 'Beverages', 'Fruit Juices & Drinks', 'B Natural', 'Juice - Litchi Luscious', 'Juices', 'NA', 'Presenting, B Natural Litchi offers an authentic litchi experience because it is made with litchi pulp. Every litchi is handpicked to ensure a superior taste in every sip of B Natural. The entire range of B Natural is crafted from Indian Fruits and Not From Concentrate. The process of developing B Natural does not use the additional step of concentration, which involves heating of juice/pulp to remove water content, which may lead to loss of fruit nutrients in the form of antioxidants, like Vitamin C.', '1', 'Ltr', '1', '110.00', '93.500', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/100076754_8-b-natural-juice-litchi-luscious.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(357, '', 'Bakery ', 'Beverages', 'Fruit Juices & Drinks', 'Maaza', 'Juice - Mango Refresh', 'Juices', 'NA', 'Maaza mango juice is one of the most popular fruit-based drinks in India. It is a real pleasure to taste the blend of real alphonso and totapuri mango pulp in the juice. Not only does it serve as a great fruity drink, it is also considered as an instant energizer because of the high sugar content. A number of innovative cocktails and mocktails can be made with Maaza mango juice.', '150', 'ML', '1', '10.00', '10.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/265725_12-maaza-juice-mango-refresh.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(358, '', 'Bakery ', 'Beverages', 'Fruit Juices & Drinks', 'Maaza', 'Juice - Mango,', 'Juices', 'NA', 'Maaza, in India, is synonymous with the very spirit of mangoes. Enjoy the deliciously thick, sweet and a delightful mango experience with a chilled glass of Maaza, a quality product of The Coca-Cola Company. Maaza, the indulging, ready-to-serve mango drink, is made from mango pulp and handpicked Alphonso. The drink is universally loved for its taste, colour, thickness and wholesome properties. This deliciously authentic mango fruit drink is the mango lover\'s first choice and if you are one, sit back and open a Maaza to experience Aam ka Magic for yourself.', '1.5', 'Ltr', '1', '80.00', '62.370', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40001001_20-maaza-juice-mango.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
