(414, '', 'Grocery', 'Beverages', 'GOURMET TEA & TEA BAGS', 'TGL Co.', 'Kadak Masala Chai Tea Bag, 64 g', 'Chai Tea', 'Tea Bag', 'Nothing can quite replace the wholesome goodness that is a cup of freshly-made chai. If you need to make your morning cuppa a refreshing one, top off your brew with some strong spices, then here\'s a cuppa comfort. \r\n\r\nWrap your hands around the customary cup of good old Indian chai blended with aromatic spices. Enjoyed by millions in India, masala chai, a spiced, sweetened black tea mixed with milk, is now popular around the world.', '64', 'GM', '16', '24.00', '189.790', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40181122_4-tgl-co-kadak-masala-chai-tea-bag.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(415, '', 'Grocery', 'Beverages', 'GOURMET TEA & TEA BAGS', 'Zevic', 'Kashmiri Kahwa', 'Chai Tea', 'NA', 'This particular tea needs no introduction, experience Kashmir’s most prized possession, and revel in the goodness of Zevic’s authentic Kashmiri Kahwa brought to you straight from the valleys. This incredibly flavourful blend is complete with Almond, Cardamom, Clove, Cinnamon, Ginger, Rose Petal & Kashmiri Saffron creating an aromatic cup of goodness that improves digestion, burns fat, builds immunity, boosts energy, accentuates skin health, actively helps keep stress at bay and has an unmatched taste. It is also packed with fibre, protein, magnesium, and vitamin E. It doesn’t end there. This box is naturally sweetened by zero-calorie, plant-based Stevia so as to avoid extra processed sugars.', '50', 'GM', '1', '249.00', '249.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40213692_1-zevic-kashmiri-kahwa.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(416, '', 'Grocery', 'Beverages', 'GOURMET TEA & TEA BAGS', 'TGL Co', 'Kashmiri Kahwa Green Tea Bag - Detox Tea Desi Kahwa', 'Chai Tea', 'Tea Bag', '\r\nParadise of spice. Our take on the renowned beverage from the Kashmir valley with its richness of Indian spices and the goodness of Green tea. The first sip of the tea transports you to the ethereal snow-clad peaks of the Himalayas. \r\n\r\nAt the second sip, the warmth of Cardamom, Cloves, and Cinnamon, reminds of a cosy evening by the bonfire. The experience is enriched by nutty nuances of almonds and slivers of Kashmiri Saffron along with the benefits of Green tea.', '32', 'GM', '16', '299.00', '224.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40181121_5-tgl-co-kashmiri-kahwa-green-tea-bag-detox-tea-desi-kahwa.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(417, '', 'Grocery', 'Beverages', 'GOURMET TEA & TEA BAGS', 'Emperia', 'Kashmiri Kahwa Tea', 'Chai Tea', 'Tea bags', 'The Emperia Premium Tea range brings unique favours to your tea. Our Kashmiri Kahwa Green Tea is made of select tender green tea leaves with a touch of Indian spices, nuts and safflower. The goodness of traditional Indian spices blended with green tea makes this a perfect drink to have post meals. Kahwa is an exotic mix of Kashmiri green tea leaves, whole spices, nuts and saffron, which was traditionally prepared in a brass kettle known as a samovar. Kahwa tea is one such beverage that is an amazing combination of delicious taste, aroma and a bundle of health benefits.', '20', 'GM', '10', '159.00', '95.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40178019_8-emperia-kashmiri-kahwa-tea.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(418, '', 'Grocery', 'Beverages', 'GOURMET TEA & TEA BAGS', 'Kapiva', 'Kashmiri Kawah Tea', 'Chai Tea', 'Tea bags', 'Kashmiri Kawah tea is an incredible combination of delicious taste and aroma. Packed with many health benefits, these green tea bags resonate with the power of Indian spices. Kashmiri Kawah is distinguished as an integral part of Kashmir\'s heritage. Because of the presence of saffron, this stress releasing tea serves as a warming drink and helps the local Kashmiris withstand the harsh winters. Kashmiri Kahwa tea is loaded with health benefits. It helps to purify the digestive system and enhances digestion. It is also famous for easing stomach related issues. It helps to prevent the deposition of cholesterol in blood vessels and aids in reducing the risk of heart diseases while burning fat. Being rich in antioxidants, Kashmiri Kawah tea helps to make you stress-free and reduces anxiety levels by neutralizing the negative effects of stress-induced toxins in the body.Kapiva Kashmiri Kawah Green Tea combines two rich legacies of India. The base tea leaves have been sourced from selected estates of Darjeeling tea. This is then combined with Kashmiri tradition so that you can easily relish a perfect cuppa. The Kawah is made by boiling almonds with saffron strands, cinnamon bark and cardamom pods. Occasionally Kashmiri roses are added to provide an extra zing to its exotic aroma. Generally, it\'s served with sugar or honey, and crushed almonds or walnuts. For ease of use, Kapiva Kashmiri Kawah Green Tea is in the form of teabags. Conveniently packed and easy to prepare, you can enjoy this hot comforting beverage that hails from the beautiful valley of Kashmir, in just minutes.', '72', 'GM', '32', '460.00', '382.500', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40186996_2-kapiva-kashmiri-kawah-tea.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(419, '', 'Grocery', 'Beverages', 'GOURMET TEA & TEA BAGS', 'Teamonk', 'Kimaya White Tea', 'Chai Tea', 'NA', 'In the Himalayan snows and high, sharp mountains, are plucked these deistic two leaves and a bud, which undergo gentle processing to produce this gourmet white tea, and exude a hue which can only be divine, thus justifying its name Kimaya, which means Divinity in Sanskrit. The buds are glorified under the winter sun and emanate a natural flavour with a pleasant aftertaste. Rich in antioxidants as well as other healthful minerals, it has a rich body and savoury aroma.', '125', 'GM', '1', '525.00', '367.500', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40187584_1-teamonk-kimaya-white-tea.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(420, '', 'Grocery', 'Beverages', 'GOURMET TEA & TEA BAGS', 'Zevic', 'Lavender Rose Herbal Tea', 'Chai Tea', 'NA', 'Lavender Rose Tea is known for its therapeutic and rejuvenating properties that can detoxify your mind and body by relieving stress and anxiety. The authentic amalgamation of premium Darjeeling green tea, Rose petals, Lavender flower and peppermint leaves gently purifies while inaugurating the process of healing from within.', '50', 'GM', '1', '249.00', '249.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40213698_1-zevic-lavender-rose-herbal-tea.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(421, '', 'Grocery', 'Beverages', 'GOURMET TEA & TEA BAGS', 'TGL Co', 'Lemon Detox Green Tea Bag Make Brew Iced Tea or Hot Tea', 'Chai Tea', 'Tea Bag', 'Your dose of daily detox! A vibrant and healthy blend of green tea rich in anti-oxidants with a zing of Lemon which will cleanse your body and revive your mind, leaving you light and rejuvenated for the day.', '32', 'GM', '16', '340.00', '244.300', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40181123_5-tgl-co-lemon-detox-green-tea-bag-make-brew-iced-tea-or-hot-tea.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(422, '', 'Grocery', 'Beverages', 'GOURMET TEA & TEA BAGS', 'Emperia', 'Lemon Ginger Herbal Infusion Tea', 'Chai Tea', 'Tea bags', '\r\nIf you\'re looking for a warm, relaxing drink with health benefits and a strong taste, lemon ginger tea may be for you. It’s a favorite among herbal tea drinkers. Our Emperia Lemon Ginger Herbal  Infusion Tea is sure to invigorate instantly.', '20', 'GM', '10', '150.00', '95.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40178014_5-emperia-lemon-ginger-herbal-infusion-tea.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
