(426, '', 'Grocery', 'Beverages', 'GOURMET TEA & TEA BAGS', 'TGL Co.', 'Mogo Mogo Green Tea Bags Make Brew Iced Tea or Hot Tea', 'Chai Tea', 'Tea Bag', 'Cheery notes of bananas, mango, melons and guava hit your palate as you take in the first sip of this absolutely happy blend. Slowly you start feeling the temporise with rhythmic, flavourful beats from passionflower leaves, cornflowers and sunflowers. The tenor of this tea is calming and uplifting all at once. Trust us, you’ll be humming to every sip with this one!', '32', 'GM', '16', '340.00', '261.750', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40181120_5-tgl-co-mogo-mogo-green-tea-bags-make-brew-iced-tea-or-hot-tea.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(427, '', 'Grocery', 'Beverages', 'GOURMET TEA & TEA BAGS', 'Teamonk', 'Nilgiri Green Tea - Seiki Peppermint', 'Chai Tea', 'NA', 'Signifying Fundamental Energy in Zen theory, this inspiring Seiki Peppermint Green tea is derived from the cool leaves of menta x Piperita, or peppermint. A cup of this invigorating tea pack is sufficient to liven you up in the wake of a monotonous day. It is prepared with carefully chosen astounding leaves at a height of 1800 meters. It experiences negligible handling and the fresh brilliant green leaves spread out when injected with water giving a fragile fragrance, and tastes smooth like the delicate unfurling leaves and dependable sweet crisp like that of a peppermint flavour that lingers.', '125', 'GM', '1', '550.00', '291.500', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40187583_1-teamonk-nilgiri-green-tea-seiki-peppermint.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(428, '', 'Grocery', 'Beverages', 'GOURMET TEA & TEA BAGS', 'Teamonk', 'Nilgiri Hozo Orange Pekoe Black Tea - Loose Leaf', 'Chai Tea', 'NA', 'Hozo, meaning hidden treasure in Zen philosophy, is one of those rare luxuries available to you in a teacup. This long, wiry black leaf tea unfolds beautifully in your kettle to yield a light orange yellow liquor, with a subtle sweet flavour. It is peerless in its taste, aroma and the experience it delivers to your body and mind.', '125', 'GM', '1', '285.00', '199.500', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40187586_1-teamonk-nilgiri-hozo-orange-pekoe-black-tea-loose-leaf.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(429, '', 'Grocery', 'Beverages', 'GOURMET TEA & TEA BAGS', 'Teamonk', 'Nilgiri Sei White Tea', 'Chai Tea', 'NA', 'Rare is the combination of beauty and purity, and our Sei White Tea is one of those rare clones. Meaning Purity in Zen philosophy, it reflects cleanliness and purity in the physical and the spiritual, along with beautiful curled leaves. Carefully picked as a leaf and a bud from the top section of the plant, the leaves undergo minimal processing. The resultant brew is a light white liquor with undertones of vegetal aroma.', '100', 'GM', '1', '950.00', '503.500', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40094026_6-teamonk-nilgiri-sei-white-tea.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(430, '', 'Grocery', 'Beverages', 'GOURMET TEA & TEA BAGS', 'Teamonk', 'Nilgiri Sei White Tea', 'Chai Tea', 'NA', 'Sei, meaning purity in Zen philosophy, reflects cleanliness and orderliness in the physical and the spiritual. Our white tea from Nilgiris is most befitting of this name due to its subtle flavour and experience that requires a stillness of mind and environment to appreciate in its entirety. Carefully handpicked as a leaf and a bud, these high grown teas have a well-defined structure and orderliness. This fragrant brew has an underlying fragrance of mint, a light and refreshing aroma followed by a soothing aftertaste. A highly prized tea with bright green leaves and silver tips, the Sei White tea brews into a light green cup of smooth, sublime tea with bold notes of spearmint. Our teas taste best in their natural form, without any milk or sugar. A little milk and sugar or honey and lime can be added to complement your taste preferences.', '100', 'GM', '50', '1375.00', '758.750', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40187595_1-teamonk-nilgiri-sei-white-tea.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(431, '', 'Grocery', 'Beverages', 'GOURMET TEA & TEA BAGS', 'Teamonk', 'Nilgiri Wa Oolong Tea', 'Chai Tea', 'Pyramic Bags', 'Harmony is not a matter of intensity, but of balance, order and rhythm; our Wa Oolong stands a true testimony to the statement. Wa, the Zen word for Harmony is all about balance, the balance between the weather and the wind, tea gardens and leaves, taste and aroma, black tea and green. Handpicked leaves from the estates in Nilgiris are allowed partial-oxidation and semi-fermentation to arrest the juice of the tea leaves. They are then extremely delicately hand-rolled which unfurl when the leaves are substracted to water.', '50', 'GM', '1', '700.00', '371.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40096761_6-teamonk-nilgiri-wa-oolong-tea.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
