(2233, '', 'Bakery', 'Snacks And Choclates ', 'Chocolate', 'Fabelle', 'Centre Filled Bar Infused With White Mousse & Chilli', 'Mousse & Chilli', 'NA', 'Bite into the dark chocolate shell to discover a silky-smooth white mousse infused with chilli. Fabelle Fire has been created with premium ingredients, where high-quality cocoa meets an exotic ingredient - Ancho chilli. Relax and unwind as you indulge in this luxurious centre-filled chocolate bar.\r\n\r\nHandcrafted by Master Chocolatiers, Fabelle Fire has been inspired by the element of fire. Dive into a mystical delight of Fabelle Fire as it sets your senses on fire. It evokes a multi-sensorial experience as it teases you with its rich aroma, smooth texture and indulgent taste. This chocolate bar is perfect as a mid-day/ post-dinner indulgence or as a cure for Monday blues. Whenever the mood strikes, irrespective of the time and day, this centre-filled luxury dark chocolate bar will lift your spirits. ', '131', 'GM', '1', '350.00', '350.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40185194_4-fabelle-fire-centre-filled-bar-infused-with-white-mousse-chilli.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(2234, '', 'Bakery', 'Snacks And Choclates ', 'Chocolate', 'Flat Tummies', 'The Protein Bar - Cocoa', 'Cocoa', 'NA', 'At Flat Tummies, we believe that “Losing your tummy can be yummy”. Our products are tastefully designed to replace junk with the healthiest alternatives. This Protein bar is made to meet the exact nutrition of 8.4g protein to a consumer as recommended per serving by nutritionists. The source of Protein is only from all natural Chia seeds, Flaxseeds and Pumpkin seeds with absolutely no compromise on taste! 100% natural with no preservative, sugar-free, gluten free, dairy free and with low calorie, this chocolate delight is diabetic friendly and suitable for all age groups. The right combination of low GI sweeteners such as dates, raisins and coconut sugar ensures a fulfilling experience without spiking the sugar levels. The exact protein from natural ingredients offers good energy and strength to move on with your daily routine without having to worry about weight gain or any side effects. This product is for the consumer who’s hustling around his day to day life, however, needs daily nutrition to feel good and feel complete.', '35', 'GM', '1', '75.00', '75.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40163864_7-flat-tummies-the-protein-bar-cocoa.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
