(2308, '', 'Bakery', 'Snacks And Choclates ', 'CARAMEL & NOUGAT BAR', 'Nestle', 'Kitkat Dessert Delight Tempting Truffle - Wafer Coated With Chocolate', 'Wafer Bar', 'NA', 'With milk chocolate coating over cocoa wafer cubes, Nestlé KitKat Dessert Delight Truffle gives you a delectable dessert experience like truffle pastry anytime you want. This tempting truffle is the ideal delightful treat when you’re in the mood for something fun and unique. Enjoying dessert delight truffle, wafer coated with milk chocolate as part of a balanced diet is one of life’s little pleasures and this Kitkat makes a perfect delicious treat with only approx. 57 calories per serving (3 cubes). So, break your way to delicious  KitKat wafer recipes or simply open up for delight in every bite!  Have A Break, Have A Kitkat. \r\n\r\nAllergens: May contain Peanuts. ', '50', 'GM', '1', '55.00', '44.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40114578_12-nestle-kitkat-dessert-delight-tempting-truffle-wafer-coated-with-chocolate.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(2309, '', 'Bakery', 'Snacks And Choclates ', 'CARAMEL & NOUGAT BAR', 'Nestle', 'Munch Crunchlicious Chocolate Coated Wafer Bar', 'Wafer Bar', 'NA', 'Nestle Munch brings to you a wafer-based crunchilicious bar resulting in an explosive multi- sensorial crunch. Munch chocolate lets you discover something new with every bite. The chocolaty crunch gives Munch a sweet and delicious taste, so you can savour every bite.\r\n\r\nAllergens: May contain Peanuts.\r\nStorage: Store in a cool, dry and hygienic place.', '25', 'GM', '1', '10.00', '10.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40018536_4-nestle-munch-crunchlicious-chocolate-coated-wafer-bar.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(2310, '', 'Bakery', 'Snacks And Choclates ', 'CARAMEL & NOUGAT BAR', 'Nestle', 'Polo - The Mint With The Hole', 'Mint', 'NA', 'Nestle\'s Polo was launched in India in 1993. Popularly known as \'The Mint with the Hole\', it has the perfect balance of sweet and mint and has earned its space as an iconic confectionery brand. It is made with the goodness of natural mint. Polo mint sweets are shaped under immense pressure - roughly equivalent to two elephants jumping on it. Polo mints\' distinct flavor comes from high-quality mint oil that is specially selected to give a smooth, clean and fresh flavor. Each roll of Polo is pocket-friendly and carries multiple bite-sized serves of a mint candy treat, so you can enjoy \'The Mint with the Hole\' on the go. Important Notice: Young children (less than 4 years) have limited chewing ability and could choke on small candies.\r\n\r\nStorage: Store in a cool, dry, and hygienic place.', '15', 'GM', '1', '5.00', '5.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/118555_11-nestle-polo-the-mint-with-the-hole.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(2311, '', 'Bakery', 'Snacks And Choclates ', 'CARAMEL & NOUGAT BAR', 'Nestle', 'Munch Crisp-Pop Chocolate Coated Crunchy Wafer,', 'Wafer Bar', 'NA', 'Nestle MUNCH CRISP POP - a first of kind variant brings to you a unique taste offering delivered through the iconic CRUNCH of MUNCH. With the subtle taste of caramel flavoured popcorn, packed in a coated wafer format Munch Crisp-Pop, discover something new with every bite. You have loved the same delicious MUNCH taste for years but now experience it with the subtlety of Caramel flavoured popcorn. Savouring chocolate as part of a balanced diet is one of life’s little pleasures and this MUNCH Crisp- Pop makes a perfect crunchy chocolaty treat with each serve of 10g (1/2 bar) containing approx. 45 kcal. So, crunch your way to mouth-watering MUNCH CRISP-POP with friends or you can also enjoy it by yourself.', '20.1', 'GM', '1', '10.00', '10.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40179751_1-nestle-munch-crisp-pop-chocolate-coated-crunchy-wafer.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
