(166, 'DB-BeveragesFruit Juices & DrinksRealAloe KiwiJuicesNA1Ltr', 'Confectionery', 'Beverages', 'Fruit Juices & Drinks', 'Real', 'Aloe Kiwi', 'Juices', 'NA', 'The goodness of aloe vera and kiwi from the house of Real, India\'s No.1 Juices and Nectar Brand. It contains numerous phytonutrients, vitamins and minerals. This drink with its unique composition has an invigorating taste that packs with it strong, nutritional and healthy protective punch.', 1, 'Ltr', 1, 110, 94, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40198202_1-real-aloe-kiwi.jpg', '0', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0),
(167, 'DB-BeveragesFruit Juices & DrinksPaper BoatAnar, Pomegranate JuiceJuicesNA1Ltr', 'Confectionery', 'Beverages', 'Fruit Juices & Drinks', 'Paper Boat', 'Anar, Pomegranate Juice', 'Juices', 'NA', 'Originally from Iran, this princely fruit descended the Silk Route to our short break’s tiffin dabbas. Anar, we’ll have you know, is quite the old hat. So old, that its first sightings have been traced to the Bronze Age. Maybe that’s why it’s so good at beating aging. And today, its nectar has been painstakingly collected and presented to you without fuss, frills, pollutants or preservatives. It would be a disservice to call it a mere drink. Anar is a liquid miracle.', 1, 'Ltr', 1, 140, 140, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40105628_5-paper-boat-anar-pomegranate-juice.jpg', '0', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0),
(168, 'DB-BeveragesFruit Juices & DrinksPaper BoatAnar, Pomegranate JuiceJuicesNA200ML', 'Confectionery', 'Beverages', 'Fruit Juices & Drinks', 'Paper Boat', 'Anar, Pomegranate Juice', 'Juices', 'NA', 'Originally from Iran, this princely fruit descended the Silk Route to our short break’s tiffin dabbas. Anar, we’ll have you know, is quite the old hat. So old, that its first sightings have been traced to the Bronze Age. Maybe that’s why it’s so good at beating aging. And today, its nectar has been painstakingly collected and presented to you without fuss, frills, pollutants or preservatives. It would be a disservice to call it a mere drink. Anar is a liquid miracle.', 200, 'ML', 1, 35, 35, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40073395_5-paper-boat-anar-pomegranate-juice.jpg', '0', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0),
(169, 'DB-BeveragesFruit Juices & DrinksPaper BoatApple Fruit JuiceJuicesNA150ML', 'Confectionery', 'Beverages', 'Fruit Juices & Drinks', 'Paper Boat', 'Apple Fruit Juice', 'Juices', 'NA', 'An apple a day keeps the doctor away’ might just be the main mantra of the Indian parent’s handbook, no? Which kid wasn’t raised with sermons on how one must eat apples for health? It’s a good thing that this biblical fruit is juicy, tasty and fulfilling or else we’d really have a bone to pick with our parents. Growing up we had a family joke, that no matter what time of the day you tell mom you’re hungry she has a standard response, ‘apple khaa lo’. In fact we reached a point where we would ask her just for this automated response and then giggle away to glory. In our household, apples were not just the breakfast fruit, however, because we made warm apple pies and trifle pudding with apple pieces regularly. The unsung hero of fruits, it truly was versatile and is the family’s go-to snack option to this day!', 150, 'ML', 1, 20, 20, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/412402_3-paper-boat-apple-fruit-juice.jpg', '0', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0),
(170, 'DB-BeveragesFruit Juices & DrinksBrewhouse Brewing Co. Organic Forest Berry Ice TeaIce TeaNA350ML', 'Confectionery', 'Beverages', 'Fruit Juices & Drinks', 'Brewhouse ', 'Brewing Co. Organic Forest Berry Ice Tea', 'Ice Tea', 'NA', 'BrewHouse Tea Brewing Co is on a mission to bring real brewed organic ice tea to those who have a passion for tea. Our Ice Teas are Brewed By Humans, Not By Machines! As a result, the flavours and goodness of our whole leaf teas, straight from the hills of the Nilgiri and Assam, are preserved for all those tea lovers in India. The tangy flavours of forest berries combined with the goodness of handpicked tea leaves, offers a unique and flavoursome way to refresh your mind, body and soul. Afterall, where else do you get completely organic ice tea with forest berries?', 350, 'ML', 1, 80, 72, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40173070_5-brewhouse-tea-brewing-co-organic-forest-berry-ice-tea.jpg', '0', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0),
(171, 'DB-BeveragesFruit Juices & DrinksBrewhouse Brewing Co. Organic Mojito Lime Ice TeaIce TeaNA350ML', 'Confectionery', 'Beverages', 'Fruit Juices & Drinks', 'Brewhouse ', 'Brewing Co. Organic Mojito Lime Ice Tea', 'Ice Tea', 'NA', 'BrewHouse Tea Brewing Co is on a mission to bring real brewed organic ice tea to those who have a passion for tea. Our Ice Teas are Brewed By Humans, Not By Machines! As a result, the flavours and goodness of our whole leaf teas, straight from the hills of the Nilgiri and Assam, are preserved for all those tea lovers in India. The sweet and sour flavours of blueberry along with the flavours of green tea, combined to offer consumers the perfect way to beat the heat. So if you\'re looking to keep cool and healthy, this is your tastiest option.', 350, 'ML', 1, 80, 72, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40173072_5-brewhouse-tea-brewing-co-organic-mojito-lime-ice-tea.jpg', '0', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0),
(172, 'DB-BeveragesFruit Juices & DrinksNescafe Intense Cafe CoffeeCafe Coffee - Ready To DrinkJuicesNA180ML', 'Confectionery', 'Beverages', 'Fruit Juices & Drinks', 'Nescafe Intense Cafe Coffee', 'Cafe Coffee - Ready To Drink', 'Juices', 'NA', 'Now indulge in your favourite, the tastiest cold coffee in this convenient on the go pack. Sip or shoot, it\'s your coffee! NESCAFE Intense brings out a delicious coffee indulgence with an invigorating kick of Cappuccino, perfect for those who enjoy their coffee strong. Discover this exciting range of Ready-to-Drink coffees from one of the world\'s biggest coffee brands, NESCAFE. This range of deliciously brewed cold coffees comes in a convenient ready to drink format in Intense Cafe and Chilled Latte flavours and tastes best when chilled._x000D_\n_x000D_\nOne of the world\'s most loved brands, NESCAFE has been making one of the world\'s most loved beverages, Coffee, for over six decades. Overall these years, NESCAFE has grown on the commitment to make your brew ever more delightful, for you to kick-start an adventure.', 180, 'ML', 1, 35, 35, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40083081_7-nescafe-ready-to-drink-coffee-flavoured-milk-intense-cafe.jpg', '0', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0),
(173, 'DB-BeveragesFruit Juices & DrinksPaper BoatChilli Guava Juice,JuicesNA150ML', 'Confectionery', 'Beverages', 'Fruit Juices & Drinks', 'Paper Boat', 'Chilli Guava Juice,', 'Juices', 'NA', 'Our chilli guava is like we took that memory, squished it, and put it in a pack just for you. And hey, here are more slow-mo shots for you to savour. Imagine the way she slices open the guava and dunks in all that masala. Imagine you having to bite the collar of your uniform just so you don’t salivate. Imagine hitching your lunch basket between your knees so that you can partake in this glorious feast with both hands. Yaaas. That’s what we’re talking about.', 150, 'ML', 1, 20, 20, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40165687_3-paper-boat-chilli-guava-juice.jpg', '0', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0),
(174, 'DB-BeveragesFruit Juices & DrinksNestle MiloCocoa-Malt Milk BeverageJuicesNA180ML', 'Confectionery', 'Beverages', 'Fruit Juices & Drinks', 'Nestle Milo', 'Cocoa-Malt Milk Beverage', 'Juices', 'NA', 'Energy is essential for growth and activity. Regular sports, with a nutritious diet, is important for an active, healthy lifestyle for children. Tasty and nutritious, Milo is the world\'s leading chocolate malt beverage that helps provide the energy to go further. Nourish your champion with Milo that has the goodness of milk, and is fortified with the goodness of vitamins and minerals. _x000D_\n_x000D_\nKids love the international taste of Milo, made with malted barley, cocoa and milk. The milk beverage also has a unique ingredient Activ-Go, which contains Protomalt, Vitamins, and minerals essential to the health and wellbeing of the body. Store in a cool, dry and hygienic place. _x000D_\n_x000D_\nServing: Shake well before drinking. Pack contains 1 serve.', 180, 'ML', 1, 35, 26, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40107707_8-nestle-milo-cocoa-malt-milk-beverage.jpg', '0', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0),
(175, 'DB-BeveragesFruit Juices & DrinksPaper BoatCoconut Water,JuicesNA200ML', 'Confectionery', 'Beverages', 'Fruit Juices & Drinks', 'Paper Boat', 'Coconut Water,', 'Juices', 'NA', 'The sweet taste of nature’s coolest hydrant is reminiscent of many evenings at the beach. We would have just enough money for one treat. After a sweaty evening filled with activities like running and playing ball, the whole bunch of cousins, elder ones being in charge, of course, would invariably end up at their favourite nariyal pani wala who would help us pick the sweetest coconuts (it’s still a mystery to me how they can always tell those ones apart). To think that all these years later, we still pick a nariyal pani to cool down on a hot summer day, that says a lot about our allegiance to this natural coolant. Sadly, there is not as much playtime anymore but as long as there’s coconut water, all we got to do is shut our eyes and be transported, giggles, laughter and all._x000D_\n_x000D_\nTo give you the best, all the coconuts are acquired from the local orchards of Coimbatore and Pollachi area of Tamil Nadu. So, it will surely become your favourite. Moreover, coconut water is packed with health benefits. It is great for hydration and keeps your body cool. Considered as a natural detoxifier by several ayurvedic studies, it works great as a stress buster also.', 200, 'ML', 1, 50, 33, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40114332_5-paper-boat-coconut-water.jpg', '0', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0),
(176, 'DB-BeveragesFruit Juices & DrinksB NaturalDakshin Pink GuavaJuicesNA750ML', 'Confectionery', 'Beverages', 'Fruit Juices & Drinks', 'B Natural', 'Dakshin Pink Guava', 'Juices', 'NA', 'The new B Natural Transparent Range. Hand-picked from the best orchards of South India, this beverage is made only from the best of Pink Guavas that are known to be pulpier and tastier than any other guava with its unique flavour. And What\'s more? This beverage is made only with 100% Indian Fruits without any concentrates, preservatives, artificial colours or flavours.', 750, 'ML', 1, 110, 105, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40165173_2-b-natural-dakshin-pink-guava.jpg', '0', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0),
(177, 'DB-BeveragesFruit Juices & DrinksFrootiFresh \'N\' Juicy MangoJuicesNA1Ltr', 'Confectionery', 'Beverages', 'Fruit Juices & Drinks', 'Frooti', 'Fresh N Juicy Mango', 'Juices', 'NA', 'Frooti Drink is completed of new juicy mangoes giving you a flavour that will remind you of the actual fruit. It is the most trusted fruit beverage brand. It portrays a humorous child-like image. Indulge yourself in a delightful juicy experience with Frooti Mango Drink, a delicious mango juice. Made from fresh, real mango pulp with no preservatives it is so full of mangoes that every sip is like biting into a real juicy mango.', 1, 'Ltr', 1, 68, 68, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/265699_2-frooti-drink-fresh-n-juicy-mango.jpg', '0', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0);
