(181, 'DB-BeveragesFruit Juices & DrinksDel MonteFruit Juice - Four SeasonsJuicesNA240ML', 'Confectionery', 'Beverages', 'Fruit Juices & Drinks', 'Del Monte', 'Fruit Juice - Four Seasons', 'Juices', 'NA', 'Del Monte Four Seasons fruit drink is made using Pineapple, Mango, Orange and Guava. Have it chilled and it is sure to refresh and delight you with its fruity goodness and exotic flavours.', 240, 'ML', 1, 60, 60, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40124303_3-del-monte-fruit-juice-four-seasons.jpg', '0', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0),
(182, 'DB-BeveragesFruit Juices & DrinksRealFruit Power - Masala SugarcaneJuicesNA180ML', 'Confectionery', 'Beverages', 'Fruit Juices & Drinks', 'Real', 'Fruit Power - Masala Sugarcane', 'Juices', 'NA', 'Sugarcane and Spicy Masala, a love story that has been part of every Indian home across generations. Real Masala Sugarcane is one of the 1st in India offering the benefits of your age-old sugarcane juice with a sprinkling of traditional Indian masala in the hygienic Tetra pack format. So relish every drop of our new Masala Sugarcane beverage that promises to refresh you with every gulp. Savour the natural sugarcane goodness brought to your home by Real.', 180, 'ML', 1, 20, 20, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40194698_1-real-fruit-power-masala-sugarcane.jpg', '0', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0),
(183, 'DB-BeveragesFruit Juices & DrinksRealFruit Power - Pink GuavaJuicesNA1Ltr', 'Confectionery', 'Beverages', 'Fruit Juices & Drinks', 'Real', 'Fruit Power - Pink Guava', 'Juices', 'NA', 'Real with its promise of Fruit Nutrition and irresistible taste has been offering the goodness of Guava over the years which has been showered by your love, making it one of the selling variants for Real. As a new story of the Real Guava Story, we bring to you the delectable premium experience of “100 % Pink Guava Product. _x000D_\n_x000D_\nReal Pink Guava is one of the 1st in-country offering the goodness of \'100% Pink Guava\', the premium variety of Guava. So savour the irresistible taste of Pink Guava along with Real\'s promise of Fruit Nutrition.', 1, 'Ltr', 1, 110, 110, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40194700_1-real-fruit-power-pink-guava.jpg', '0', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0),
(184, 'DB-BeveragesFruit Juices & DrinksRealFruit Power Juice - Alphonso MangoJuicesNA1Ltr', 'Confectionery', 'Beverages', 'Fruit Juices & Drinks', 'Real', 'Fruit Power Juice - Alphonso Mango', 'Juices', 'NA', 'If mango is considered the king of fruits, then Alphonso is surely the king of kings. Every sip of Alphonso is a royal experience with a taste that makes you long for more. Much more. So lose yourself in the heavenly natural goodness of Real Alphonso and savour our promise of nothing but taste & happiness. The best part is there is no added preservatives, artificial colour and artificial flavours.', 1, 'Ltr', 1, 120, 120, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40128989_3-real-fruit-power-juice-alphonso-mango.jpg', '0', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0),
(185, 'DB-BeveragesFruit Juices & DrinksRealFruit Power Juice - AppleJuicesNA1Ltr', 'Confectionery', 'Beverages', 'Fruit Juices & Drinks', 'Real', 'Fruit Power Juice - Apple', 'Juices', 'NA', 'They do say an apple a day keeps the doctor away, but we often overlook the fact that it also keeps the children away! Especially after the apples have been cut and kept out for some time. Discover the joy of Apple – the kids will love it. The crisp delight of apples can be felt in every sip of Réal Fruit Power Apple. And yes, it\'s good for your child\'s active lifestyle too. It is packed with energy and provides your child with the nutrition equivalent to a glass of milk. Combine this with its signature yummy taste, and Réal Fruit Power Apple becomes your one-step solution to your child\'s fussy eating habits. It’s Réal Fruit Power for your kid and complete peace of mind for you, all the way, anywhere and everywhere you need it. It comes with no added colour or preservatives and is sealed with the latest and the best six layered Tetra Pak packaging that retains the freshness of the beverage like a freshly picked fruit. It is this consistent effort that has helped us become India\'s most trusted brand in the food and beverages category.', 1, 'Ltr', 1, 105, 85, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/265854_4-real-fruit-power-juice-apple.jpg', '0', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0),
(186, 'DB-BeveragesFruit Juices & DrinksRealFruit Power Juice - GrapeJuicesNA1Ltr', 'Confectionery', 'Beverages', 'Fruit Juices & Drinks', 'Real', 'Fruit Power Juice - Grape', 'Juices', 'NA', 'Real Grape Juice is prepared from the greatest quality sweet grapes to make sure consistent quality around the year. A refreshing drink for occasions like mid-morning and late afternoon.', 1, 'Ltr', 2, 210, 191, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/1209504_4-real-fruit-power-juice-grape.jpg', '0', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0),
(187, 'DB-BeveragesFruit Juices & DrinksRealFruit Power Juice - GuavaJuicesNA1Ltr', 'Confectionery', 'Beverages', 'Fruit Juices & Drinks', 'Real', 'Fruit Power Juice - Guava', 'Juices', 'NA', 'Blessed with numerous nutrients of nature, the \'Pink\' guava is well known for its great taste and endless health benefits. Every day, we pick, create and share only the best quality of pink guavas straight from the foothills of Karnataka. The supreme taste and goodness of the ‘pink’ guavas are packed into each pack of Réal Guava. It’s not just the colour pink, but the aroma, nutrition and taste of the rarest of Pink guavas of the Deccan plateau that makes Réal guava unique. We bring to life not only the tastiest of the beverages but also the healthiest. This is ensured by a six-layered Tetra Pak that keeps all germs, air, sunlight and harmful UV rays away. The packaging helps it stay protected from harmful bacteria, preserve the nutritive value and keeps it fresh till the last sip just like any other guava juice.', 1, 'Ltr', 1, 100, 67, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/229930_2-real-fruit-power-juice-guava.jpg', '0', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0),
(188, 'DB-BeveragesFruit Juices & DrinksRealFruit Power Juice - MangoJuicesNA1Ltr', 'Confectionery', 'Beverages', 'Fruit Juices & Drinks', 'Real', 'Fruit Power Juice - Mango', 'Juices', 'NA', 'Réal Fruit Power Mango is the ultimate indulgence. It\'s thick and so full of mangoes that every sip is like biting into the sumptuous fruit itself. The best part is that even when the king of fruits has retired for the season, the goodness and joy of Mangoes continues to live on in households across India, thanks to Réal Fruit Power Mango. Poured over cubes of ice, mixed with milk into a shake or sipped straight from the pack, it never ceases to delight.', 1, 'Ltr', 1, 100, 91, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/229912_2-real-fruit-power-juice-mango.jpg', '0', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0),
(189, 'DB-BeveragesFruit Juices & DrinksRealFruit Power Juice - Masala GuavaJuicesNA1Ltr', 'Confectionery', 'Beverages', 'Fruit Juices & Drinks', 'Real', 'Fruit Power Juice - Masala Guava', 'Juices', 'NA', 'Since childhood, we have enjoyed guava with a dash of mouth-watering chatpata masala. So we decided to take the same old guava magic and bring it to you in a way you will love, with Real Masala Guava. Each sip is full of fruit goodness and a taste so exciting that it will make you go GUA- WAAH!_x000D_\n_x000D_\nMade from the best quality fruits, Réal Fruit juice has no added preservatives; hence it offers not just taste, but also Fruit Power - the power to stay ahead. Réal’s ingredients are endorsed by PFNDAI (Protein Foods & Nutrition Development Association of India) to produce only the finest quality of fruit juice in India. This comes to you in an aseptic 6-layered Tetra Pak which ensures that the juice has all of the all the goodness and nutrition of the fruit when it reaches you.', 1, 'Ltr', 1, 105, 105, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40128987_2-real-fruit-power-juice-masala-guava.jpg', '0', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0),
