(244, 'DB-BeveragesGOURMET TEA & TEA BAGSKarma KettleBenares Authentic Indian Masala Chai - Loose LeafChai TeaLoose Leaf100GM', 'Confectionery', 'Beverages', 'GOURMET TEA & TEA BAGS', 'Karma Kettle', 'Benares Authentic Indian Masala Chai - Loose Leaf', 'Chai Tea', 'Loose Leaf', 'Our signature blend will transport you to the busy streets of Benares-staying true to its name! Assam Black tea is blended with an array ofspices (cinnamon, cardamom, ginger, cloves) to create a bold infusion that is full of flavour_x000D_\n_x000D_\nChai Nation- Fun facts on India\'s favourite brew_x000D_\n_x000D_\n\'Chai\' is undoubtedly one of the most popular drinks in India, it is typically served in attractive clay cups in roadside stalls and is an essential part of Indian culture._x000D_\nThere a so many recipes of chai the most popular being the Kadak Street style masala chai to the Kesar or Saffron Masala Chai_x000D_\nSome chai recipescontain over 15 different types of spices_x000D_\nThe spices used in preparing masala chai to boost our immunity, improve digestion and benefit in overall wellness', 100, 'GM', 1, 350, 350, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40134939_2-karma-kettle-benares-authentic-indian-masala-chai-loose-leaf.jpg', '0', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0),
(245, 'DB-BeveragesGOURMET TEA & TEA BAGSChaayosChai Masala - Spice BlendChai TeaNA100GM', 'Confectionery', 'Beverages', 'GOURMET TEA & TEA BAGS', 'Chaayos', 'Chai Masala - Spice Blend', 'Chai Tea', 'NA', 'Chaayos Chai Masla is a unique blend of aromatic spices which are specially crafted to impact a perfect Masala Flavour to Chai. The balance of flavours is based on Chaayos\'s rich experience of making the Ghar Wali Chai. Just add a pinch to your regular chai while making and dive into a journey of exceptional flavour.', 100, 'GM', 1, 249, 219, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40194561_1-chaayos-chai-masala-spice-blend.jpg', '0', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0),
(246, 'DB-BeveragesGOURMET TEA & TEA BAGSVAHDAMChamomile Lavender Green Tea Bags - Calming Tea For SleepChai TeaTea bags30GM', 'Confectionery', 'Beverages', 'GOURMET TEA & TEA BAGS', 'VAHDAM', 'Chamomile Lavender Green Tea Bags - Calming Tea For Sleep', 'Chai Tea', 'Tea bags', 'The quintessential soothing nightcap fortified with the antioxidant goodness of Green Tea. Buoyant chamomile and lavender work together to offer a soothing detox effect and help induce sleep while helping you destress. Relish a light pale yellow liquoring cup with sweet floral notes that travel throughout the cup.', 30, 'GM', 15, 225, 191, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40207940_1-vahdam-chamomile-lavender-green-tea-bags-calming-tea-for-sleep.jpg', '0', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0),
(247, 'DB-BeveragesGOURMET TEA & TEA BAGSTeamonkDarjeeling Ahina Long Leaf Green TeaChai TeaNA100GM', 'Confectionery', 'Beverages', 'GOURMET TEA & TEA BAGS', 'Teamonk', 'Darjeeling Ahina Long Leaf Green Tea', 'Chai Tea', 'NA', 'The state of being perfectly well in body, soul (mind, will and emotions) and spirit, is nothing but the feeling of being Whole; just like our Ahina Whole Leaf Green Tea. A completely non-fermented tea, the leaves remain whole until the time you brew it. Two leaves and a bud are picked by adept tea pluckers and carefully carried for processing. They are handled with gentleness and care to ensure their high quality is maintained. The resultant brew that flows into your cup is a smooth, gleaming tea that reflects the keen spirit of this special tea with a fresh, aromatic flavour.', 100, 'GM', 1, 550, 291, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40094013_6-teamonk-darjeeling-ahina-long-leaf-green-tea.jpg', '0', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0),
(248, 'DB-BeveragesGOURMET TEA & TEA BAGSTeamonkDarjeeling Oolong Tea - TapasChai TeaNA125GM', 'Confectionery', 'Beverages', 'GOURMET TEA & TEA BAGS', 'Teamonk', 'Darjeeling Oolong Tea - Tapas', 'Chai Tea', 'NA', 'When you nurture a leaf in the most intricate way possible so that what you get is a delicate, handcrafted tea with the best of its essence, you can call it nothing but penance. And what is a better name for this leaf tea than Tapas, its Sanskrit synonym? Two leaves and a bud are plucked from the choicest tea gardens in Darjeeling and carried for processing where it is only allowed partial oxidation. The result is a tea that proudly balances between the matured blacks and subtle greens.', 125, 'GM', 1, 525, 368, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40187579_1-teamonk-darjeeling-oolong-tea-tapas.jpg', '0', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0),
(249, 'DB-BeveragesGOURMET TEA & TEA BAGSTeamonkDarjeeling Reeti White TeaChai TeaNA100GM', 'Confectionery', 'Beverages', 'GOURMET TEA & TEA BAGS', 'Teamonk', 'Darjeeling Reeti White Tea', 'Chai Tea', 'NA', 'If belonging to nature was a virtue, Reeti White Tea would be the unambiguous winner. Of nature, for nature and completely true to its nature, this tea is the right name for natural propensity in Sanskrit. The delicate Pak ho buds are plucked by thin nimble fingers to produce this exquisite white tea. The processing enriches it with the goodness of nature, combined with sun-drying and pan-frying, giving a tea that brims with vitality.', 100, 'GM', 1, 875, 875, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40094025_6-teamonk-darjeeling-reeti-white-tea.jpg', '0', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0),
(250, 'DB-BeveragesGOURMET TEA & TEA BAGSTeamonkDarjeeling Reeti White TeabagsChai TeaTea Bag50GM', 'Confectionery', 'Beverages', 'GOURMET TEA & TEA BAGS', 'Teamonk', 'Darjeeling Reeti White Teabags', 'Chai Tea', 'Tea Bag', 'If belonging to nature was a virtue, Reeti White Tea would be the unambiguous winner. Of nature, for nature and completely true to its nature, this tea is the right name for Natural Propensity in Sanskrit. The delicate \'Pak ho\' buds are plucked by thin nimble fingers to produce this exquisite white tea. The processing enriches it with the goodness of nature, combined with sun-drying and pan-frying, giving a tea that brims with vitality.', 50, 'GM', 25, 875, 463, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40136537_2-teamonk-darjeeling-reeti-white-teabags.jpg', '0', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0);
