ing garbage. \r\nThis helps prevent the spread of bacteria and germs, keeping you and your family healthy. \r\nEven when you are out of the home and do not have water and soap available, carry an alcohol-based sanitizing gel. \r\nBathe regularly, that is, wash your body and your hair often after intervals that suit you. \r\nUsing Dettol soap on the skin can help minimize dryness and help keep germs away for a healthier you. \r\nUnclean skin can cause not only over-the -skin problems but also internal problems leading to illness and diseases. \r\nBrush and floss, ideally after every meal. At the very least, brush your teeth twice a day and floss daily, which can minimize the accumulation of bacteria ', '1.5', 'L', '1', '200.00', '188.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40160740_14-dettol-hand-wash-liquid-refill-skincare.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
