(310, 'Bakery ', 'Beverages', 'Fruit Juices & Drinks', 'Real', 'Aloe Kiwi', 'Juices', 'NA', 'The goodness of aloe vera and kiwi from the house of Real, India\'s No.1 Juices and Nectar Brand. It contains numerous phytonutrients, vitamins and minerals. This drink with its unique composition has an invigorating taste that packs with it strong, nutritional and healthy protective punch.', '1', 'Ltr', '1', '110.00', '93.500', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40198202_1-real-aloe-kiwi.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(311, 'Bakery ', 'Beverages', 'Fruit Juices & Drinks', 'Paper Boat', 'Anar, Pomegranate Juice', 'Juices', 'NA', 'Originally from Iran, this princely fruit descended the Silk Route to our short break’s tiffin dabbas. Anar, we’ll have you know, is quite the old hat. So old, that its first sightings have been traced to the Bronze Age. Maybe that’s why it’s so good at beating aging. And today, its nectar has been painstakingly collected and presented to you without fuss, frills, pollutants or preservatives. It would be a disservice to call it a mere drink. Anar is a liquid miracle.', '1', 'Ltr', '1', '140.00', '140.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40105628_5-paper-boat-anar-pomegranate-juice.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
