(365, 'Bakery ', 'Beverages', 'Fruit Juices & Drinks', 'Paper Boat', 'Lychee Ras, Litchi JuicE', 'Juices', 'NA', 'Growing up, this scaly fruit fascinated all of us. A magic fruit that\'s hard from the outside but super soft on the inside, is a fruit but could easily pass for a dessert. Yup! That\'s Lychee for you! While the taste of lychee was hard not to love, peeling it was a total mood kill. Being the baby of the family we would get away with a lot of things and lychee-peeling ceremony was definetly one of them. Eating lychees while sitting around in our night suits post-dinner. Maa peeling at this tropical wonder with an extra fan (vintage, fished out from storage) pointed in our direction is how I shall forever remember childhood summers. The sweet, fleshy fruit still evokes that same sense of happy, lazy summer nostalgia in me. Thank God for juice though, no pleading about peeling necessary!', '150', 'ML', '1', '20.00', '20.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40114331_11-paper-boat-lychee-ras-litchi-juice.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(366, 'Bakery ', 'Beverages', 'Fruit Juices & Drinks', 'Real', 'Mango Drink', 'Juices', 'NA', 'Enjoy the lip-smacking taste of your favourite mango drink from the house of Real, India\'s no.1 juices and nectar brand. Real brings to you the new Real mango drinks made from hand-picked mangoes. This fruit beverage so thick with mangoes that each gulp of it is like biting deep into the tender goodness of ripe, juicy mangoes.', '250', 'ML', '1', '20.00', '17.600', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40195382_1-real-mango-drink.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
