(388, 'Grocery', 'Beverages', 'GOURMET TEA & TEA BAGS', 'Karma Kettle', 'Benares Authentic Indian Masala Chai - Loose Leaf', 'Chai Tea', 'Loose Leaf', 'Our signature blend will transport you to the busy streets of Benares-staying true to its name! Assam Black tea is blended with an array ofspices (cinnamon, cardamom, ginger, cloves) to create a bold infusion that is full of flavour\r\n\r\nChai Nation- Fun facts on India\'s favourite brew\r\n\r\n\'Chai\' is undoubtedly one of the most popular drinks in India, it is typically served in attractive clay cups in roadside stalls and is an essential part of Indian culture.\r\nThere a so many recipes of chai the most popular being the Kadak Street style masala chai to the Kesar or Saffron Masala Chai\r\nSome chai recipescontain over 15 different types of spices\r\nThe spices used in preparing masala chai to boost our immunity, improve digestion and benefit in overall wellness', '100', 'GM', '1', '350.00', '350.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40134939_2-karma-kettle-benares-authentic-indian-masala-chai-loose-leaf.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
