(390, 'Grocery', 'Beverages', 'GOURMET TEA & TEA BAGS', 'VAHDAM', 'Chamomile Lavender Green Tea Bags - Calming Tea For Sleep', 'Chai Tea', 'Tea bags', 'The quintessential soothing nightcap fortified with the antioxidant goodness of Green Tea. Buoyant chamomile and lavender work together to offer a soothing detox effect and help induce sleep while helping you destress. Relish a light pale yellow liquoring cup with sweet floral notes that travel throughout the cup.', '30', 'GM', '15', '225.00', '191.250', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40207940_1-vahdam-chamomile-lavender-green-tea-bags-calming-tea-for-sleep.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(391, 'Grocery', 'Beverages', 'GOURMET TEA & TEA BAGS', 'Teamonk', 'Darjeeling Ahina Long Leaf Green Tea', 'Chai Tea', 'NA', 'The state of being perfectly well in body, soul (mind, will and emotions) and spirit, is nothing but the feeling of being Whole; just like our Ahina Whole Leaf Green Tea. A completely non-fermented tea, the leaves remain whole until the time you brew it. Two leaves and a bud are picked by adept tea pluckers and carefully carried for processing. They are handled with gentleness and care to ensure their high quality is maintained. The resultant brew that flows into your cup is a smooth, gleaming tea that reflects the keen spirit of this special tea with a fresh, aromatic flavour.', '100', 'GM', '1', '550.00', '291.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40094013_6-teamonk-darjeeling-ahina-long-leaf-green-tea.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(392, 'Grocery', 'Beverages', 'GOURMET TEA & TEA BAGS', 'Teamonk', 'Darjeeling Oolong Tea - Tapas', 'Chai Tea', 'NA', 'When you nurture a leaf in the most intricate way possible so that what you get is a delicate, handcrafted tea with the best of its essence, you can call it nothing but penance. And what is a better name for this leaf tea than Tapas, its Sanskrit synonym? Two leaves and a bud are plucked from the choicest tea gardens in Darjeeling and carried for processing where it is only allowed partial oxidation. The result is a tea that proudly balances between the matured blacks and subtle greens.', '125', 'GM', '1', '525.00', '367.500', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40187579_1-teamonk-darjeeling-oolong-tea-tapas.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
