(437, 'Grocery', 'Beverages', 'GOURMET TEA & TEA BAGS', 'Karma Kettle', 'Nolen Gur & Khejur Chai - Loose Leaf,', 'Chai Tea', 'Loose Leaf,', '\r\nOur signature blend pays tribute to Kolkata with a delicious sinful combination of black tea with nolen gur( Bengal palm jaggery) & premium dates. This tea releases an irresistible caramel aroma. On the palate you will get a decadent toffee flavour with creamy notes- reminiscent of a sticky toffee date pudding. Finish is rich, smooth and well rounded.', '75', 'GM', '1', '400.00', '400.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40134938_6-karma-kettle-nolen-gur-khejur-chai-loose-leaf.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(438, 'Grocery', 'Beverages', 'GOURMET TEA & TEA BAGS', 'Chaayos', 'nstant Tea Premix - Masala, Regular Sugar', 'Chai Tea', 'Sachet', '\r\nNow travel anywhere with your Ready-to-Make Chai. You crave for it. We got it. A ready-to-make powder mix that contains a blend of natural extracts of finest tea leaves and Indian spices complemented by the stimulating flavours of cardamom, cloves, black pepper and ginger; finished with the subtlety of Cinnamon and Nutmeg, and added sugar and milk powder. Use it while travelling anytime, anywhere, at your own convenience!', '110', 'GM', '5', '125.00', '125.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40194789_1-chaayos-instant-tea-premix-masala-regular-sugar.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(439, 'Grocery', 'Beverages', 'GOURMET TEA & TEA BAGS', 'Emperia', 'Orange Spice Green Tea,', 'Chai Tea', 'Tea bags', 'The Emperia Premium Tea range brings unique flavours to your tea. Our Orange Spice Green Tea is made of a blend of select green tea leaves with orange peel and a strong note of spices. The zesty orange flavour infused with the goodness of traditional spices is all you need to spice up your day.', '20', 'GM', '10', '150.00', '95.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40178018_7-emperia-orange-spice-green-tea.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(440, 'Grocery', 'Beverages', 'GOURMET TEA & TEA BAGS', 'TGL Co.', 'Organic Green Tea Bag', 'Chai Tea', 'Tea Bag', 'For the connoisseurs who appreciate tea in its purest essence, here\'s a pure, soothing cup of organic green tea to cherish. Grown with utmost care using artisanal methods of production, these minimally oxidised green tea leaves are loaded with anti-oxidants and reveal a nourishing brew with fresh, soothing and uplifting vegetal notes.', '32', 'GM', '16', '240.00', '174.300', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40181125_5-tgl-co-organic-green-tea-bag.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(441, 'Grocery', 'Beverages', 'GOURMET TEA & TEA BAGS', 'Lumiere', 'Organic Malli Kappi', 'Chai Tea', 'NA', 'Lumiere is one of the pioneers in Organic agriculture, Cooking, Baking & Retailing. A simple homemade Immunity Booster, Malli Kappi, is a herbal alternative to normal tea/coffee for many. Full of natural remedy spices like Coriander Seeds, dried Ginger (Chukku), Black Pepper, Cardamom, Cumin Seeds, Fenugreek and Clove, this herbal recipe has a magical character to cure Cold, cough and headache. Regular use of Mall Kappi improves digestion too. One can use Jaggery or Palm Jaggery or Palm Sugar as a sweetener in this recipe.', '50', 'GM', '1', '130.00', '130.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40206601_1-lumiere-organic-malli-kappi.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
