(443, 'Grocery', 'Beverages', 'GOURMET TEA & TEA BAGS', 'Isvaari', 'Peach Breeze Loose Black Tea with Real Peaches', 'Chai Tea', 'NA', 'Peach tea contains powerful antioxidants that can help to fight the signs of aging skin. Peach tea Improved metabolism also helps in burning calories and thus, aiding weight loss. Our Isvaari Peach Green Tea has a smooth great taste and refreshing aroma.', '50', 'GM', '1', '325.00', '325.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40206682_1-isvaari-peach-breeze-loose-black-tea-with-real-peaches.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
