(446, 'Grocery', 'Beverages', 'GOURMET TEA & TEA BAGS', 'Zevic', 'Premium Green Herbal Tea For Glowing Skin', 'Chai Tea', 'NA', 'Awaken in your inner glow and achieve the perfect #NoFilter look with Zevic’s Skin Glow Tea. Bringing together ingredients like Rose Petals, Calendula, Rosemary Leaves, Lavender Flower, Pudina Leaves, Sage, and Chamomile, this beautiful blend is anti-inflammatory, combats ageing, improves skin and hair, and is a powerhouse of antioxidants that help fight off free radicals. This is naturally sweetened by zero-calorie, plant-based Stevia. Enjoy this guilt-free tea with an uncompromised taste!', '50', 'GM', '1', '249.00', '249.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40213693_1-zevic-premium-green-herbal-tea-for-glowing-skin.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(447, 'Grocery', 'Beverages', 'GOURMET TEA & TEA BAGS', 'Isvaari', 'Super Cozy Loose Flavored Green Tea With Jasmine Buds', 'Chai Tea', 'NA', 'Feel straight into your tea time. Sip tea in style as black adds a whole feel to your next round of tea. Did we tell you, these make an awesome and thoughtful gift for your loved ones too? Whether you want to serve tea at your home or at office.', '50', 'GM', '1', '45.00', '208.250', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40206687_1-isvaari-super-cozy-loose-flavored-green-tea-with-jasmine-buds.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL);
