(449, 'Grocery', 'Beverages', 'GOURMET TEA & TEA BAGS', 'Emperia', 'Tropical Fruit Infusion/Flavoured Tea', 'Chai Tea', 'Tea bags', 'The Emperia Premium Tea range brings unique flavours to your tea. Our Tropical Fruit Black Tea is made with a unique combination of tropical fruits, lemongrass and the finest black tea leaves from Assam. Known for its sweet flavour and floral aroma, it is best served with a light snack. Lemongrass, also called citronella, has a fresh, lemony aroma and a citrus flavour. You will never look for any other tea once you have delighted your senses with this amazing combination. This refreshing tea is one of the most popular ways to enjoy lemongrass.', '20', 'GM', '10', '140.00', '95.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40178005_8-emperia-tropical-fruit-infusionflavoured-tea.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
