(507, 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Fresho', 'Green Capsicum', 'Green Capsicum', 'NA', 'Leaving a moderately pungent taste on the tongue, Green capsicums, also known as green peppers are bell shaped, medium-sized fruit pods.', '500', 'GM', '1', '32.50', '26.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000069_20-fresho-capsicum-green.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(508, 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Fresho', 'Green Zucchini', 'Zucchini - Green', 'NA', 'Zucchini is a long, slender, cucumber like green vegetable that is also called squash. The green variant has a firm flesh and a mild flavour.', '500', 'GM', '1', '68.75', '55.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000123_15-fresho-zucchini-green.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(509, 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Fresho', 'Knol Khol', 'Knol Khol', 'NA', 'Knol Khols are big, greenish white colored vegetables with long, green extrusions.They have a crispy texture and taste mildly sweet', '500', 'GM', '1', '20.00', '14.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000278_12-fresho-knol-khol.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(510, 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Fresho', 'Lemon', 'Lemon', 'NA', 'With a segmented flesh that has a unique pleasant aroma and a strong sour taste, lemons are round/oval and have a yellow, texturized external peel.', '250', 'GM', '1', '16.88', '10.890', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000127_17-fresho-lemon.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(511, 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Fresho', 'Manglore Cucumber', 'Cucumber - Mangalore', 'NA', 'Mangalore cucumber is oval shaped, with yellow stripes on green background and a white, firm flesh with edible seeds. It is a sambar cucumber as it is widely used to prepare sambar in Mangalore. can be consumed raw and be used for wide number of recipes like sambar, curries, chutney, dosa, idli, Mangalore cucumber raitha, etc.', '1', 'KG', '1', '18.75', '10.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000100_9-fresho-cucumber-mangalore.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(512, 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Fresho', 'Mushroom', 'Mushrooms - Button', 'NA', 'Buttom mushrooms are very small sized mushrooms with smooth round caps and short stems. They have a mild flavour with a good texture that becomes more fragrant and meaty when cooked.', '1', 'PAK', '1', '61.25', '40.590', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000273_16-fresho-mushrooms-button.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(513, 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Fresho', 'Onion', 'Onion', 'NA', 'Onion is a vegetable which is almost like a staple in Indian food. This is also known to be one of the essential ingredients of raw salads. They come in different colours like white, red or yellow and are quite in demand in cold salads and hot soups.\r\n You can dice, slice or cut it in rings and put it in burgers and sandwiches. Onions emit a sharp flavour and fragrance once they are fried; it is due to the sulphur compound in the vegetable.Onions are known to be rich in biotin.\r\n Most of the flavonoids which are known as anti-oxidants are concentrated more in the outer layers, so when you peel off the layers, you should remove as little as possible.', '1', 'KG', '1', '33.75', '25.740', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000148_30-fresho-onion.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(514, 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Fresho', 'Parwal', 'Parwal', 'NA', 'With a yellowish green skin, Parwal is short, slightly pointed at one end and blunt on the other. The flesh of this vegetable is creamy white with small and firm seeds.\r\n It has a bland flavour, allowing it to absorb a variety of flavours from spices while cooking.', '500', 'GM', '1', '92.50', '67.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000366_10-fresho-parwal.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(515, 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Fresho', 'Peeled Garlic', 'Garlic - Peeled', 'NA', 'Fresho provides you peeled garlic for your convenience and ease.', '200', 'GM', '1', '91.25', '73.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/30005201_4-fresho-garlic-peeled.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(516, 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Fresho', 'Potato', 'Potato', 'NA', 'Fresho Potatoes are nutrient-dense, non-fattening and have reasonable amount of calories. Include them in your regular meals so that the body receives a good supply of carbohydrates, dietary fibers and essential minerals such as copper, magnesium, and iron. In India, potatoes are probably the second-most consumed vegetables after onions.', '1', 'KG', '1', '32.50', '20.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000159_25-fresho-potato.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(517, 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Fresho', 'Potato', 'Baby Potato', 'NA', 'These small baby potatoes are a sweeter variety than normal ones and come with a creamy off white interior. Baby potato is a starchy vegetable that adds thickness to recipes and blends well with other vegetables.', '500', 'GM', '1', '31.25', '19.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000024_20-fresho-baby-potato.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(518, 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Fresho', 'Pumpkin', 'Pumpkin - Organically Grown', 'NA', 'It is organically grown and handpicked from farm\r\n Product image shown is for representation purpose only, the actually product may vary based on season, produce & availability.', '1', 'PCS', '1', '111.25', '62.310', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40023471_4-fresho-pumpkin-organically-grown.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(519, 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Fresho', 'Pumpkin', 'Pumpkin - Disco', 'NA', 'The pumpkins have a smooth, yellowish-orange skin with a creamish to orange coloured flesh that has a pleasant squash-like taste. Their flat, edible seeds (pepitas) are tender and mildly sweet.\r\n Fresho is our brand of fresh fruits and vegetables which are individually handpicked every day by our experienced and technically competent buyers.\r\n Our buying, storing and packaging processes are tailored to ensure that only the fresh, nutrient-dense, healthy and delicious produce reaches your doorstep.\r\n We guarantee the quality of all Fresho products.If you\'re not satisfied with the freshness of the items, you can hand them back to our Customer Experience Executive (CEE) for a full refund.', '1', 'PCS', '1', '62.50', '49.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40202912_1-fresho-pumpkin-disco.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(520, 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Fresho', 'Radish White', 'Radish - White', 'NA', 'Radishes are a root crop with a crunchy texture and a sharp, spicy, hot or sweet taste. They are juicy and sometimes have a pungent smell.', '500', 'GM', '1', '20.00', '8.910', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000166_16-fresho-radish-white.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(521, 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Fresho', 'Raw Banana', 'Banana - Raw Green', 'NA', 'Raw bananas are unripened bananas with a tough, green skin. Their flesh is white, dense and has a starchy-tart flavour.\r\n We selectively pick organically grown raw green bananas from the best farms.', '500', 'GM', '1', '25.00', '20.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000168_13-fresho-banana-raw-green.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(522, 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Fresho', 'Red Capsicum', 'Capsicum - Red, Organically Grown', 'NA', 'Red capsicums are thin, smooth skinned, crunchy, mildly sweet tasting, hollow vegetables that are juicier variants of the green capsicum. They are perfect for adding a dash of colour, distinct taste and beautiful scent to your salad, pizza, pasta or even gravy preparations. They are sourced directly from farmers, so that you receive only the best quality ones which not only jazz up any dish but also offer health benefits. Product image shown is for representation purpose only, the actual product may vary based on season, produce & availability. Click here for delicious vegetable recipes - https://www.bigbasket.com/flavors/collections/227/fresh-vegetables/', '1', 'PCS', '1', '35.00', '28.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40124625_1-fresho-capsicum-red-organically-grown.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(523, 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Fresho', 'Ridge Gourd', 'Ridge Gourd', 'NA', 'Ridge Gourds are long vegetables with a ridged dark green skin and white spongy flesh that contains numerous seeds inside.\r\n They are rich in fiber and very prominent in Indian cooking.', '1', 'KG', '1', '73.50', '73.500', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000175_15-fresho-ridge-gourd.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(524, 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Fresho', 'Sambhar Onion (Small Onion)', 'Sambhar Onion (Small Onion)', 'NA', 'Onion can fill your kitchen with a thick spicy aroma. It is a common base vegetable in most Indian dishes, thanks to the wonderful flavor that it adds to any dish.Also known as button onions, Sambar Onions are relatively smaller onions with a mild flavour and slightly sweet taste.', '250', 'GM', '1', '31.25', '19.550', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000178_12-fresho-sambhar-onion-small-onion.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(525, 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Fresho', 'Snake Gourd', 'Snake Gourd', 'NA', 'Snake gourds are true to their name as they have a long, curved shape with light green speckles and a waxy green skin.\r\n Their firm flesh is embedded with seeds and they taste like cucumber and have a slightly bitter taste.\r\n The fruits are orange in colour when ripe and pulpy red after complete ripening.', '500', 'GM', '1', '13.75', '10.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000185_11-fresho-snake-gourd.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(526, 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Fresho', 'Spring Onion', 'Spring Onion', 'NA', 'Spring onions come with a crisp texture and sweet flavor.\r\n They are moist with thin, white flesh and a green stem.\r\n The green stems are hollow, bitter, and pungent.', '100', 'GM', '1', '12.50', '3.960', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/20000981_6-fresho-spring-onion.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(527, 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Fresho', 'Sweet Potato', 'Sweet Potato', 'NA', 'With flesh colours ranging from white, orange and yellow, sweet potatoes are ovate and cylindrical with golden brown or white-brown skin and a delicious sweet flavour.\r\n While the white fleshed are firm, orange fleshed are softer.', '500', 'GM', '1', '30.00', '15.840', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000194_13-fresho-sweet-potato.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(528, 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Fresho', 'Tender Coconut', 'Tender Coconut - Medium', 'NA', 'Young, fresh and healthy tender coconuts are a pure, tasty and nutritious energy drink that keeps body hydrated round the clock.\r\n Tender coconut is the most refreshing drink and best to quench your thirst in the summer.\r\n Tender coconut has antioxidant properties which help to protect the body from free radicals.\r\n It helps to lower blood pressure level, prevent kidney stone, and support heart health.', '1', 'PCS', '1', '57.50', '46.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40057966_2-fresho-tender-coconut-medium.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(529, 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Fresho', 'Tender Coconut', 'Tender Coconut - Small', 'NA', 'Young, fresh and healthy tender coconuts are a pure, tasty and nutritious energy drink that keeps body hydrated round the clock.\r\n Tender coconut is the most refreshing drink and best to quench your thirst in the summer.\r\n Tender coconut has antioxidant properties which help to protect the body from free radicals.\r\n It helps to lower blood pressure level, prevent kidney stone, and support heart health.', '1', 'PCS', '1', '55.00', '44.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40073760_3-fresho-tender-coconut-small.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(530, 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Fresho', 'Tinda', 'Tinda', 'NA', 'Tinda is a small vegetable that looks bigger than a green apple but smaller than a pumpkin.\r\n Short and squat like a pumpkin, tindas have a dark green stem and white flesh that is tender and tastes like a cucumber.\r\n The seeds within are edible.', '500', 'GM', '1', '93.75', '75.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000371_11-fresho-tinda.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(531, 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Fresho', 'Tomato Hybrid', 'Tomato - Hybrid', 'NA', 'omato Hybrids are high-quality fruits compared to desi, local tomatoes. They contain numerous edible seeds and are red in colour due to lycopene, an anti-oxidant.', '1', 'KG', '1', '17.50', '14.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000200_17-fresho-tomato-hybrid.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(532, 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Fresho', 'Tomato Local', 'Tomato - Local', 'NA', 'Local tomatoes are partly sour and partly sweet and contain many seeds inside which are edible. The red colour present in tomatoes is due to lycopene, an anti-oxidant.', '1', 'KG', '1', '23.75', '13.860', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000203_16-fresho-tomato-local.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(533, 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Fresho', 'Yellow Capsicum', 'Capsicum - Yellow', 'NA', 'Capsicum is wealthy in several phytonutrients especially antioxidants, minerals and dietary fibre like manganese, copper, potassium and magnesium. It is wealthy in Vitamin A, B6, C, E, K and has small amounts of thiamine, niacin and folate. It adds a dynamic personality to your food owing to a vibrant yellow colour. It mixes into any dish and brings out a certain zing and taste. It is a storehouse of vital nutrients.', '2', 'PCS', '2', '43.75', '35.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40149661_1-fresho-capsicum-yellow.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(534, 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Fresho', 'Yellow Zucchini', 'Zucchini - Yellow', 'NA', 'Yellow zucchini is a long and slightly fat vegetable, also known as squash. Yellow variant has comparatively softer flesh and tastes sweeter than the green one.', '500', 'GM', '1', '68.75', '55.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000211_16-fresho-zucchini-yellow.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(535, 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Leafy Items', 'Fresho', 'Coriander', 'Coriander Leaves', 'NA', 'Coriander leaves are green, fragile with a decorative appearance. They contain minimal aroma and have a spicy sweet taste.Now do not bother wasting time cutting off the roots as we value your money and time and provide you the freshest leafy edible parts .', '100', 'GM', '1', '12.50', '6.930', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000097_19-fresho-coriander-leaves.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(536, 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Leafy Items', 'Fresho', 'Curry Leaves', 'Curry Leaves', 'NA', 'Curry leaves are an essential element of Indian cooking style where numerous of the traditional and modern recipes are imperfect without curry leaves.These are used as tasting agent in food for its different taste.With dark green and glossy appearance, curry leaves have a strong flavour and release a tasty aroma when fried in hot oil.', '100', 'GM', '1', '12.50', '4.960', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000104_17-fresho-curry-leaves.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(537, 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Leafy Items', 'Fresho', 'Dill Leaves', 'Dill Leaves', 'NA', 'Green, flimsy and fernlike Dill leaves have a strong aroma. sharp tang and a spongy sugary flavour. Dill leaves are rich in nutritional value. They help enhance digestion, prevent insomnia, manage diabetes. Regular addition of Dill leaves in your diet will help you on the long run. You can also make dill pickles and use it as a healthy accompaniment.', '100', 'GM', '1', '10.00', '8.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40207906_2-fresho-dill-leaves.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(538, 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Leafy Items', 'Fresho', 'Fenugreek', 'Methi/Venthaya Keerai', 'NA', 'Methi leaves are a very popular ingredient in Indian dishes that has a bitter taste and strong aroma.', '250', 'GM', '1', '35.00', '28.000', 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000112_17-fresho-methiventhaya-keerai.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL);
