(80, 5, 'zaSBHA', 493, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh VegitablesFreshoCauliflowerCauliflowerNA1PCS', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Fresho', 'Cauliflower', 'Cauliflower', 'NA', 'Cauliflower is made up of tightly bound clusters of soft, crumbly, sweet cauliflower florets that form a dense head.Resembling a classic tree, the florets are attached to a central edible white trunk which is firm and tender.', 1, 'PCS', 1, 52, 42, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000074_19-fresho-cauliflower.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-05 00:00:00', '2022-01-05 00:00:00', 0, 0),
