(134, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2817, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh FruitsGreen houseButter FruitAvocadoNA2PCS', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Fruits', 'Green house', 'Butter Fruit', 'Avocado', 'NA', 'Avocado is an oval-shaped fruit with thick green and a bumpy, leathery outer skin. They have a unique texture, with a creamy and light green colored flesh that has a buttery flavour and a special aroma. Avocados are also known as alligator pear or butter fruit. These avocados delivered to you, will not just entice your taste buds but will also ensure your well being. The approximate weight of one avocado is around 300-500 g.', 2, 'PCS', 2, 165, 132, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40202915_9-fresho-indian-avocado-butterfruit.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-05 00:00:00', '2022-01-05 00:00:00', 0, 0),
(135, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2818, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh FruitsGreen houseGrapes - Bangalore Blue with SeedGrapes - Bangalore Blue with SeedNA500GM', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Fruits', 'Green house', 'Grapes - Bangalore Blue with Seed', 'Grapes - Bangalore Blue with Seed', 'NA', 'Exclusively grown in Chikkaballapur, Bangalore Urban and Kolar districts, these soft skinned Fresho black blue grapes have a foxy flavour and a brisky pungent taste.\r\n We have neatly packed the best quality grapes to make your day fresh and healthy.', 500, 'GM', 1, 55, 44, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/20000707_12-fresho-grapes-bangalore-blue-with-seed.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-05 00:00:00', '2022-01-05 00:00:00', 0, 0),
(136, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2819, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh FruitsGreen houseGrapes - Red Globe IndianGrapes - Red Globe IndianNA500GM', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Fruits', 'Green house', 'Grapes - Red Globe Indian', 'Grapes - Red Globe Indian', 'NA', 'Ruby-coloured Fresho red globe grapes are uniquely large, round and good quality grapes. They have a crunchy skin, fleshy pulp and a pinkish tinge in colour. The grapes have mild sweetness and taste, but these grapes are not as tangy as flame seedless or as sweet as Thompson seedless.', 500, 'GM', 1, 136, 109, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40019777_3-fresho-grapes-red-globe-indian.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-05 00:00:00', '2022-01-05 00:00:00', 0, 0),
(137, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2820, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh FruitsGreen houseGrapes Sonaka SeedlessGrapes - GreenNA500GM', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Fruits', 'Green house', 'Grapes Sonaka Seedless', 'Grapes - Green', 'NA', 'Juicy and snappy, with a beautiful balance of sweet and tarty flavour, these grape bunches have a lingering taste.Do not tire yourselves searching for unspoiled fruit, we have handpicked and finely packed fresho green seedless grapes which are just a few clicks away.', 500, 'GM', 1, 135, 135, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40218332_1-fresho-grapes-green.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-05 00:00:00', '2022-01-05 00:00:00', 0, 0),
(138, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2821, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh FruitsGreen houseGuava - Organically GrownGuava - Organically GrownNA500GM', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Fruits', 'Green house', 'Guava - Organically Grown', 'Guava - Organically Grown', 'NA', 'Savour the green guavas along with hard, pale yellow edible seeds.The off-white flesh is crunchy and mildly sweet with very good fragrance.We selectively pick organically grown guavas from the best farms', 500, 'GM', 1, 38, 30, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/50000518_8-fresho-guava-organically-grown.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-05 00:00:00', '2022-01-05 00:00:00', 0, 0),
(139, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2822, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh FruitsGreen houseKiwiKiwi - Green,NA3PCS', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Fruits', 'Green house', 'Kiwi', 'Kiwi - Green,', 'NA', 'Kiwis are oval shaped with a brownish outer skin. The flesh is bright green and juicy with tiny, edible black seeds. With its distinct sweet-sour taste and a pleasant smell, it tastes like strawberry and honeydew melon.', 3, 'PCS', 3, 136, 98, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/20000911_30-fresho-kiwi-green.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-05 00:00:00', '2022-01-05 00:00:00', 0, 0),
(140, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2823, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh FruitsGreen houseMusk MelonMuskmelon - StripedNA1PCS', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Fruits', 'Green house', 'Musk Melon', 'Muskmelon - Striped', 'NA', 'Fresho striped muskmelons have a distinct external skin that is smooth, with green ribbing on pistachio-grey colored surface. Their flesh is orange coloured, sweet with a floral aroma. Fresho muskmelons are directly procured from our farmers.', 1, 'PCS', 1, 43, 43, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40073761_7-fresho-muskmelon-striped.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-05 00:00:00', '2022-01-05 00:00:00', 0, 0),
