(150, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2833, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh FruitsGreen houseWatermelon KiranWatermelon - Small (1.7 - 2.5 kg)NA1PCS', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Fruits', 'Green house', 'Watermelon Kiran', 'Watermelon - Small (1.7 - 2.5 kg)', 'NA', 'With greenish black to smooth dark green surface, Fresho watermelons are globular in shape and are freshly picked for you directly from our farmers\r\n The juicy, sweet and grainy textured flesh is filled with 12-14% of sugar content, making it a healthy alternative to sugary carbonated drinks. Flesh colour of these watermelons are pink to red with dark brown/black seeds.', 1, 'PCS', 1, 116, 91, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000207_19-fresho-watermelon-small.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-05 00:00:00', '2022-01-05 00:00:00', 0, 0),
