(208, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2891, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh VegitablesGreen houseYellow CapsicumCapsicum - YellowNA2PCS', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Green house', 'Yellow Capsicum', 'Capsicum - Yellow', 'NA', 'Capsicum is wealthy in several phytonutrients especially antioxidants, minerals and dietary fibre like manganese, copper, potassium and magnesium. It is wealthy in Vitamin A, B6, C, E, K and has small amounts of thiamine, niacin and folate. It adds a dynamic personality to your food owing to a vibrant yellow colour. It mixes into any dish and brings out a certain zing and taste. It is a storehouse of vital nutrients.', 2, 'PCS', 2, 44, 35, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40149661_1-fresho-capsicum-yellow.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-05 00:00:00', '2022-01-05 00:00:00', 0, 0),
