(257, 5, 'gTQpZW', 2812, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh FruitsGreen houseApple GalaGALANA4PCS', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Fruits', 'Green house', 'Apple Gala', 'GALA', 'NA', 'Royal Gala Apples are characterized by a blush of pink of the skin, the color varies from yellow to nearly orange with deep orange stripes.It can be eaten new, taked in in salads or used as a cooking apple and is mostly suited to sauce.It is dense, sugary, sweet-smelling and juicy with a white flesh. It is an extremely special dessert apple with wonderful look.Product image shown is for representation purpose only, the actually product may vary based on season, produce & availability.', 4, 'PCS', 4, 182, 146, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000005_27-fresho-apple-royal-gala-economy.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(258, 5, 'gTQpZW', 2813, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh FruitsGreen houseApple IraniRed DeliciousNA4PCS', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Fruits', 'Green house', 'Apple Irani', 'Red Delicious', 'NA', 'The bright red coloured and heart shaped Red Delicious apples are crunchy, juicy and slightly sweet.Red Delicious Apples are a natural source of fibre and are fat free. They contain a wide variety of anti-oxidants and polynutrients.', 4, 'PCS', 4, 231, 184, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40033824_19-fresho-apple-red-delicious-regular.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(259, 5, 'gTQpZW', 2814, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh FruitsGreen houseApple RegularFuji, RegularNA4PCS', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Fruits', 'Green house', 'Apple Regular', 'Fuji, Regular', 'NA', 'A fruit specially for the ones with a sweet tooth, Fuji apples are the sweetest apples around and come with a hint of vanilla flavour.These hybrid apples have creamy white, firm and finely grained flesh.These apples are crisp, juicy and sugary. Premium apples are handpicked by our experts to give you the best quality apples.', 4, 'PCS', 4, 223, 140, '', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(260, 5, 'gTQpZW', 2815, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh FruitsGreen houseBanana RobustaRobustaNA1KG', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Fruits', 'Green house', 'Banana Robusta', 'Robusta', 'NA', 'Relish the soft, buttery texture of Robusta bananas that are light green and have a great fragrance and taste. The stalks of Robustas are thick and rigid. Fresh fruits are green, which revolve to a bright yellow on ripening and the flesh contains a white - ceramic colour.Fresho Robusta is fine quality, sweet flavoured, mushy and soft bananas.', 1, 'KG', 1, 38, 28, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000025_24-fresho-banana-robusta.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(261, 5, 'gTQpZW', 2816, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh FruitsGreen houseBanana YelakkiYelakkiNA1KG', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Fruits', 'Green house', 'Banana Yelakki', 'Yelakki', 'NA', 'Tiny and small sized, this variety is called Yelakki in Bangalore and Elaichi in Mumbai. Despite its small size, they are naturally flavoured, aromatic and sweeter compared to regular bananas.Yelakki bananas are around 3- 4 inches long and contain a thinner skin and better shelf life than Robusta bananas.', 1, 'KG', 1, 81, 65, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000031_21-fresho-banana-yelakki.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(262, 5, 'gTQpZW', 2817, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh FruitsGreen houseButter FruitAvocadoNA2PCS', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Fruits', 'Green house', 'Butter Fruit', 'Avocado', 'NA', 'Avocado is an oval-shaped fruit with thick green and a bumpy, leathery outer skin. They have a unique texture, with a creamy and light green colored flesh that has a buttery flavour and a special aroma. Avocados are also known as alligator pear or butter fruit. These avocados delivered to you, will not just entice your taste buds but will also ensure your well being. The approximate weight of one avocado is around 300-500 g.', 2, 'PCS', 2, 165, 132, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40202915_9-fresho-indian-avocado-butterfruit.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(263, 5, 'gTQpZW', 2818, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh FruitsGreen houseGrapes - Bangalore Blue with SeedGrapes - Bangalore Blue with SeedNA500GM', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Fruits', 'Green house', 'Grapes - Bangalore Blue with Seed', 'Grapes - Bangalore Blue with Seed', 'NA', 'Exclusively grown in Chikkaballapur, Bangalore Urban and Kolar districts, these soft skinned Fresho black blue grapes have a foxy flavour and a brisky pungent taste.\r\n We have neatly packed the best quality grapes to make your day fresh and healthy.', 500, 'GM', 1, 55, 44, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/20000707_12-fresho-grapes-bangalore-blue-with-seed.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(264, 5, 'gTQpZW', 2819, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh FruitsGreen houseGrapes - Red Globe IndianGrapes - Red Globe IndianNA500GM', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Fruits', 'Green house', 'Grapes - Red Globe Indian', 'Grapes - Red Globe Indian', 'NA', 'Ruby-coloured Fresho red globe grapes are uniquely large, round and good quality grapes. They have a crunchy skin, fleshy pulp and a pinkish tinge in colour. The grapes have mild sweetness and taste, but these grapes are not as tangy as flame seedless or as sweet as Thompson seedless.', 500, 'GM', 1, 136, 109, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40019777_3-fresho-grapes-red-globe-indian.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
