(267, 5, 'gTQpZW', 2822, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh FruitsGreen houseKiwiKiwi - Green,NA3PCS', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Fruits', 'Green house', 'Kiwi', 'Kiwi - Green,', 'NA', 'Kiwis are oval shaped with a brownish outer skin. The flesh is bright green and juicy with tiny, edible black seeds. With its distinct sweet-sour taste and a pleasant smell, it tastes like strawberry and honeydew melon.', 3, 'PCS', 3, 136, 98, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/20000911_30-fresho-kiwi-green.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
