(322, 5, 'gTQpZW', 2877, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh VegitablesGreen housePumpkinPumpkin - DiscoNA1PCS', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Green house', 'Pumpkin', 'Pumpkin - Disco', 'NA', 'The pumpkins have a smooth, yellowish-orange skin with a creamish to orange coloured flesh that has a pleasant squash-like taste. Their flat, edible seeds (pepitas) are tender and mildly sweet.\r\n Fresho is our brand of fresh fruits and vegetables which are individually handpicked every day by our experienced and technically competent buyers.\r\n Our buying, storing and packaging processes are tailored to ensure that only the fresh, nutrient-dense, healthy and delicious produce reaches your doorstep.\r\n We guarantee the quality of all Fresho products.If you\'re not satisfied with the freshness of the items, you can hand them back to our Customer Experience Executive (CEE) for a full refund.', 1, 'PCS', 1, 63, 49, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40202912_1-fresho-pumpkin-disco.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(323, 5, 'gTQpZW', 2878, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh VegitablesGreen houseRadish WhiteRadish - WhiteNA500GM', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Green house', 'Radish White', 'Radish - White', 'NA', 'Radishes are a root crop with a crunchy texture and a sharp, spicy, hot or sweet taste. They are juicy and sometimes have a pungent smell.', 500, 'GM', 1, 20, 9, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000166_16-fresho-radish-white.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(324, 5, 'gTQpZW', 2879, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh VegitablesGreen houseRaw BananaBanana - Raw GreenNA500GM', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Green house', 'Raw Banana', 'Banana - Raw Green', 'NA', 'Raw bananas are unripened bananas with a tough, green skin. Their flesh is white, dense and has a starchy-tart flavour.\r\n We selectively pick organically grown raw green bananas from the best farms.', 500, 'GM', 1, 25, 20, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000168_13-fresho-banana-raw-green.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(325, 5, 'gTQpZW', 2880, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh VegitablesGreen houseRed CapsicumCapsicum - Red, Organically GrownNA1PCS', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Green house', 'Red Capsicum', 'Capsicum - Red, Organically Grown', 'NA', 'Red capsicums are thin, smooth skinned, crunchy, mildly sweet tasting, hollow vegetables that are juicier variants of the green capsicum. They are perfect for adding a dash of colour, distinct taste and beautiful scent to your salad, pizza, pasta or even gravy preparations. They are sourced directly from farmers, so that you receive only the best quality ones which not only jazz up any dish but also offer health benefits. Product image shown is for representation purpose only, the actual product may vary based on season, produce & availability. Click here for delicious vegetable recipes - https://www.bigbasket.com/flavors/collections/227/fresh-vegetables/', 1, 'PCS', 1, 35, 28, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40124625_1-fresho-capsicum-red-organically-grown.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(326, 5, 'gTQpZW', 2881, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh VegitablesGreen houseRidge GourdRidge GourdNA1KG', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Green house', 'Ridge Gourd', 'Ridge Gourd', 'NA', 'Ridge Gourds are long vegetables with a ridged dark green skin and white spongy flesh that contains numerous seeds inside.\r\n They are rich in fiber and very prominent in Indian cooking.', 1, 'KG', 1, 74, 74, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000175_15-fresho-ridge-gourd.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(327, 5, 'gTQpZW', 2882, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh VegitablesGreen houseSambhar Onion (Small Onion)Sambhar Onion (Small Onion)NA250GM', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Green house', 'Sambhar Onion (Small Onion)', 'Sambhar Onion (Small Onion)', 'NA', 'Onion can fill your kitchen with a thick spicy aroma. It is a common base vegetable in most Indian dishes, thanks to the wonderful flavor that it adds to any dish.Also known as button onions, Sambar Onions are relatively smaller onions with a mild flavour and slightly sweet taste.', 250, 'GM', 1, 31, 20, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000178_12-fresho-sambhar-onion-small-onion.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(328, 5, 'gTQpZW', 2883, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh VegitablesGreen houseSnake GourdSnake GourdNA500GM', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Green house', 'Snake Gourd', 'Snake Gourd', 'NA', 'Snake gourds are true to their name as they have a long, curved shape with light green speckles and a waxy green skin.\r\n Their firm flesh is embedded with seeds and they taste like cucumber and have a slightly bitter taste.\r\n The fruits are orange in colour when ripe and pulpy red after complete ripening.', 500, 'GM', 1, 14, 10, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000185_11-fresho-snake-gourd.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
