(421, 5, 'gTQpZW', 2888, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh VegitablesGreen houseTindaTindaNA500GM', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Green house', 'Tinda', 'Tinda', 'NA', 'Tinda is a small vegetable that looks bigger than a green apple but smaller than a pumpkin.\r\n Short and squat like a pumpkin, tindas have a dark green stem and white flesh that is tender and tastes like a cucumber.\r\n The seeds within are edible.', 500, 'GM', 1, 94, 75, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000371_11-fresho-tinda.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(422, 5, 'gTQpZW', 2889, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh VegitablesGreen houseTomato HybridTomato - HybridNA1KG', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Green house', 'Tomato Hybrid', 'Tomato - Hybrid', 'NA', 'omato Hybrids are high-quality fruits compared to desi, local tomatoes. They contain numerous edible seeds and are red in colour due to lycopene, an anti-oxidant.', 1, 'KG', 1, 18, 14, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000200_17-fresho-tomato-hybrid.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(423, 5, 'gTQpZW', 2890, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh VegitablesGreen houseTomato LocalTomato - LocalNA1KG', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Green house', 'Tomato Local', 'Tomato - Local', 'NA', 'Local tomatoes are partly sour and partly sweet and contain many seeds inside which are edible. The red colour present in tomatoes is due to lycopene, an anti-oxidant.', 1, 'KG', 1, 24, 14, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000203_16-fresho-tomato-local.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(424, 5, 'gTQpZW', 2891, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh VegitablesGreen houseYellow CapsicumCapsicum - YellowNA2PCS', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Green house', 'Yellow Capsicum', 'Capsicum - Yellow', 'NA', 'Capsicum is wealthy in several phytonutrients especially antioxidants, minerals and dietary fibre like manganese, copper, potassium and magnesium. It is wealthy in Vitamin A, B6, C, E, K and has small amounts of thiamine, niacin and folate. It adds a dynamic personality to your food owing to a vibrant yellow colour. It mixes into any dish and brings out a certain zing and taste. It is a storehouse of vital nutrients.', 2, 'PCS', 2, 44, 35, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40149661_1-fresho-capsicum-yellow.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(425, 5, 'gTQpZW', 2892, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh VegitablesGreen houseYellow ZucchiniZucchini - YellowNA500GM', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Green house', 'Yellow Zucchini', 'Zucchini - Yellow', 'NA', 'Yellow zucchini is a long and slightly fat vegetable, also known as squash. Yellow variant has comparatively softer flesh and tastes sweeter than the green one.', 500, 'GM', 1, 69, 55, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000211_16-fresho-zucchini-yellow.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(426, 5, 'gTQpZW', 2893, 'Fruites and VegitablesLeafy ItemsGreen houseCorianderCoriander LeavesNA100GM', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Leafy Items', 'Green house', 'Coriander', 'Coriander Leaves', 'NA', 'Coriander leaves are green, fragile with a decorative appearance. They contain minimal aroma and have a spicy sweet taste.Now do not bother wasting time cutting off the roots as we value your money and time and provide you the freshest leafy edible parts .', 100, 'GM', 1, 13, 7, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000097_19-fresho-coriander-leaves.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(427, 5, 'gTQpZW', 2894, 'Fruites and VegitablesLeafy ItemsGreen houseCurry LeavesCurry LeavesNA100GM', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Leafy Items', 'Green house', 'Curry Leaves', 'Curry Leaves', 'NA', 'Curry leaves are an essential element of Indian cooking style where numerous of the traditional and modern recipes are imperfect without curry leaves.These are used as tasting agent in food for its different taste.With dark green and glossy appearance, curry leaves have a strong flavour and release a tasty aroma when fried in hot oil.', 100, 'GM', 1, 13, 5, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000104_17-fresho-curry-leaves.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(428, 5, 'gTQpZW', 2895, 'Fruites and VegitablesLeafy ItemsGreen houseDill LeavesDill LeavesNA100GM', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Leafy Items', 'Green house', 'Dill Leaves', 'Dill Leaves', 'NA', 'Green, flimsy and fernlike Dill leaves have a strong aroma. sharp tang and a spongy sugary flavour. Dill leaves are rich in nutritional value. They help enhance digestion, prevent insomnia, manage diabetes. Regular addition of Dill leaves in your diet will help you on the long run. You can also make dill pickles and use it as a healthy accompaniment.', 100, 'GM', 1, 10, 8, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40207906_2-fresho-dill-leaves.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(429, 5, 'gTQpZW', 2896, 'Fruites and VegitablesLeafy ItemsGreen houseFenugreekMethi/Venthaya KeeraiNA250GM', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Leafy Items', 'Green house', 'Fenugreek', 'Methi/Venthaya Keerai', 'NA', 'Methi leaves are a very popular ingredient in Indian dishes that has a bitter taste and strong aroma.', 250, 'GM', 1, 35, 28, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000112_17-fresho-methiventhaya-keerai.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
