(609, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2812, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh FruitsGreen houseApple GalaGALANA4PCS', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Fruits', 'Green house', 'Apple Gala', 'GALA', 'NA', 'Royal Gala Apples are characterized by a blush of pink of the skin, the color varies from yellow to nearly orange with deep orange stripes.It can be eaten new, taked in in salads or used as a cooking apple and is mostly suited to sauce.It is dense, sugary, sweet-smelling and juicy with a white flesh. It is an extremely special dessert apple with wonderful look.Product image shown is for representation purpose only, the actually product may vary based on season, produce & availability.', 4, 'PCS', 4, 182, 146, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000005_27-fresho-apple-royal-gala-economy.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(610, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2813, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh FruitsGreen houseApple IraniRed DeliciousNA4PCS', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Fruits', 'Green house', 'Apple Irani', 'Red Delicious', 'NA', 'The bright red coloured and heart shaped Red Delicious apples are crunchy, juicy and slightly sweet.Red Delicious Apples are a natural source of fibre and are fat free. They contain a wide variety of anti-oxidants and polynutrients.', 4, 'PCS', 4, 231, 184, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40033824_19-fresho-apple-red-delicious-regular.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(611, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2814, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh FruitsGreen houseApple RegularFuji, RegularNA4PCS', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Fruits', 'Green house', 'Apple Regular', 'Fuji, Regular', 'NA', 'A fruit specially for the ones with a sweet tooth, Fuji apples are the sweetest apples around and come with a hint of vanilla flavour.These hybrid apples have creamy white, firm and finely grained flesh.These apples are crisp, juicy and sugary. Premium apples are handpicked by our experts to give you the best quality apples.', 4, 'PCS', 4, 223, 140, '', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(612, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2815, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh FruitsGreen houseBanana RobustaRobustaNA1KG', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Fruits', 'Green house', 'Banana Robusta', 'Robusta', 'NA', 'Relish the soft, buttery texture of Robusta bananas that are light green and have a great fragrance and taste. The stalks of Robustas are thick and rigid. Fresh fruits are green, which revolve to a bright yellow on ripening and the flesh contains a white - ceramic colour.Fresho Robusta is fine quality, sweet flavoured, mushy and soft bananas.', 1, 'KG', 1, 38, 28, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000025_24-fresho-banana-robusta.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(613, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2816, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh FruitsGreen houseBanana YelakkiYelakkiNA1KG', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Fruits', 'Green house', 'Banana Yelakki', 'Yelakki', 'NA', 'Tiny and small sized, this variety is called Yelakki in Bangalore and Elaichi in Mumbai. Despite its small size, they are naturally flavoured, aromatic and sweeter compared to regular bananas.Yelakki bananas are around 3- 4 inches long and contain a thinner skin and better shelf life than Robusta bananas.', 1, 'KG', 1, 81, 65, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000031_21-fresho-banana-yelakki.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(614, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2817, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh FruitsGreen houseButter FruitAvocadoNA2PCS', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Fruits', 'Green house', 'Butter Fruit', 'Avocado', 'NA', 'Avocado is an oval-shaped fruit with thick green and a bumpy, leathery outer skin. They have a unique texture, with a creamy and light green colored flesh that has a buttery flavour and a special aroma. Avocados are also known as alligator pear or butter fruit. These avocados delivered to you, will not just entice your taste buds but will also ensure your well being. The approximate weight of one avocado is around 300-500 g.', 2, 'PCS', 2, 165, 132, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40202915_9-fresho-indian-avocado-butterfruit.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(615, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2818, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh FruitsGreen houseGrapes - Bangalore Blue with SeedGrapes - Bangalore Blue with SeedNA500GM', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Fruits', 'Green house', 'Grapes - Bangalore Blue with Seed', 'Grapes - Bangalore Blue with Seed', 'NA', 'Exclusively grown in Chikkaballapur, Bangalore Urban and Kolar districts, these soft skinned Fresho black blue grapes have a foxy flavour and a brisky pungent taste.\r\n We have neatly packed the best quality grapes to make your day fresh and healthy.', 500, 'GM', 1, 55, 44, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/20000707_12-fresho-grapes-bangalore-blue-with-seed.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(616, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2819, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh FruitsGreen houseGrapes - Red Globe IndianGrapes - Red Globe IndianNA500GM', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Fruits', 'Green house', 'Grapes - Red Globe Indian', 'Grapes - Red Globe Indian', 'NA', 'Ruby-coloured Fresho red globe grapes are uniquely large, round and good quality grapes. They have a crunchy skin, fleshy pulp and a pinkish tinge in colour. The grapes have mild sweetness and taste, but these grapes are not as tangy as flame seedless or as sweet as Thompson seedless.', 500, 'GM', 1, 136, 109, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40019777_3-fresho-grapes-red-globe-indian.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(617, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2820, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh FruitsGreen houseGrapes Sonaka SeedlessGrapes - GreenNA500GM', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Fruits', 'Green house', 'Grapes Sonaka Seedless', 'Grapes - Green', 'NA', 'Juicy and snappy, with a beautiful balance of sweet and tarty flavour, these grape bunches have a lingering taste.Do not tire yourselves searching for unspoiled fruit, we have handpicked and finely packed fresho green seedless grapes which are just a few clicks away.', 500, 'GM', 1, 135, 135, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40218332_1-fresho-grapes-green.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(618, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2821, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh FruitsGreen houseGuava - Organically GrownGuava - Organically GrownNA500GM', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Fruits', 'Green house', 'Guava - Organically Grown', 'Guava - Organically Grown', 'NA', 'Savour the green guavas along with hard, pale yellow edible seeds.The off-white flesh is crunchy and mildly sweet with very good fragrance.We selectively pick organically grown guavas from the best farms', 500, 'GM', 1, 38, 30, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/50000518_8-fresho-guava-organically-grown.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(619, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2822, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh FruitsGreen houseKiwiKiwi - Green,NA3PCS', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Fruits', 'Green house', 'Kiwi', 'Kiwi - Green,', 'NA', 'Kiwis are oval shaped with a brownish outer skin. The flesh is bright green and juicy with tiny, edible black seeds. With its distinct sweet-sour taste and a pleasant smell, it tastes like strawberry and honeydew melon.', 3, 'PCS', 3, 136, 98, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/20000911_30-fresho-kiwi-green.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(620, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2823, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh FruitsGreen houseMusk MelonMuskmelon - StripedNA1PCS', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Fruits', 'Green house', 'Musk Melon', 'Muskmelon - Striped', 'NA', 'Fresho striped muskmelons have a distinct external skin that is smooth, with green ribbing on pistachio-grey colored surface. Their flesh is orange coloured, sweet with a floral aroma. Fresho muskmelons are directly procured from our farmers.', 1, 'PCS', 1, 43, 43, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40073761_7-fresho-muskmelon-striped.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(621, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2824, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh FruitsGreen houseMusk MelonMuskmelon - Organically GrownNA1PCS', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Fruits', 'Green house', 'Musk Melon', 'Muskmelon - Organically Grown', 'NA', 'Fresho Organic products are organically grown and handpicked by expert.\r\n Product image shown is for representation purpose only, the actually product may vary based on season, produce & availability.', 1, 'PCS', 1, 50, 40, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/50000534_12-fresho-muskmelon-organically-grown.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(622, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2825, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh FruitsGreen houseMuskmelon - Netted SmallMuskmelon - Netted SmallNA1PCS', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Fruits', 'Green house', 'Muskmelon - Netted Small', 'Muskmelon - Netted Small', 'NA', 'Having a netlike/ reticulated skin covering, its a round melon with firm, orange, moderately sweet flesh and a thin, reticulated, light-grey rind.', 1, 'PCS', 1, 61, 24, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000141_24-fresho-muskmelon-netted-small.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(623, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2826, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh FruitsGreen houseOrange - ImportedOrange - ImportedNA4PCS', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Fruits', 'Green house', 'Orange - Imported', 'Orange - Imported', 'NA', 'Fresho brings you an assortment of 4 imported oranges, which make for an ideal gift during the festive season or even for making desserts and juices. These imported oranges are much bigger in size as compared to the Indian counterpart. You will notice their skin is much brighter and vibrant too. Easy to peel, these oranges are a healthy snack alternative.', 4, 'PCS', 4, 138, 110, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/20000909_18-fresho-orange-imported.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(624, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2827, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh FruitsGreen houseOrange - ImportedOrange - ImportedNA6PCS', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Fruits', 'Green house', 'Orange - Imported', 'Orange - Imported', 'NA', 'Navel oranges are very sugary and juicy and considered to be the world\'s finest orange for fresh consumption because they are very sweet, naturally juice, seedless and peels and segments very easily. It has a variety of phytochemicals containing flavanoids hesperetin, beta-carotene and carotenoids alpha etc. It is wealthy in Vitamin C, A and Folate and includes small amounts of Vitamin E & B complex vitamins too.\r\n Product image shown is for representation purpose only, the actually product may vary based on season, produce & availability.', 6, 'PCS', 6, 203, 162, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/20000910_12-fresho-orange-imported.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(625, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2828, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh FruitsGreen housePapayaPapaya SmallNA1PCS', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Fruits', 'Green house', 'Papaya', 'Papaya Small', 'NA', 'Papayas grow in tropical climates and are also known as papaws or pawpaws. Initially green and somewhat bitter in taste, papayas are butter-yellow when fully ripe and shaped like a pear.\r\n Their pale-orange flesh has dozens of small, black, sticky seeds at the center, similar to a melon.', 1, 'PCS', 1, 38, 30, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40114961_3-fresho-papaya-small.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(626, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2829, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh FruitsGreen housePapayaPapaya MediumNA1PCS', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Fruits', 'Green house', 'Papaya', 'Papaya Medium', 'NA', 'Semi ripe papayas have blend of sweet buttery consistency and sour taste. They are half green and half yellow.\r\n Ripe papaya have orange flesh and black coloured seeds at the centre.', 1, 'PCS', 1, 50, 27, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000152_18-fresho-papaya-medium.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(627, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2830, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh FruitsGreen housePapayaPapaya LargeNA1PCS', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Fruits', 'Green house', 'Papaya', 'Papaya Large', 'NA', 'Papayas are large and pear shaped with green to butter yellow skin colour when ripe.\r\n The flesh is pale orange with numerous small, black, sticky seeds at the center.\r\n They have a musky taste and buttery consistency.', 1, 'PCS', 1, 55, 44, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40125301_4-fresho-papaya-large.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(628, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2831, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh FruitsGreen housePomegranate KesarPomegranateNA4PCS', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Fruits', 'Green house', 'Pomegranate Kesar', 'Pomegranate', 'NA', 'With ruby color and an intense floral, sweet-tart flavor, the pomegranate delivers both taste and beauty.\r\n You can remove the skin and the membranes to get at the delicious fruit with nutty seeds.\r\n Fresho Pomegranates are finely sorted and graded to deliver the best tasting pomegranates to you.', 4, 'PCS', 4, 161, 129, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000269_28-fresho-pomegranate.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(629, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2832, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh FruitsGreen houseSapotaSapotaNA500GM', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Fruits', 'Green house', 'Sapota', 'Sapota', 'NA', 'Brown skinned sapotas are smooth to grainy textured, musky-scented and deliciously sweet in taste.\r\n The flesh generally contains 2-3 large and inedible black seeds. Fresho sapotas are freshly plucked by our farmers and the best quality is delivered to you.', 500, 'GM', 1, 63, 63, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000181_12-fresho-sapota.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(630, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2833, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh FruitsGreen houseWatermelon KiranWatermelon - Small (1.7 - 2.5 kg)NA1PCS', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Fruits', 'Green house', 'Watermelon Kiran', 'Watermelon - Small (1.7 - 2.5 kg)', 'NA', 'With greenish black to smooth dark green surface, Fresho watermelons are globular in shape and are freshly picked for you directly from our farmers\r\n The juicy, sweet and grainy textured flesh is filled with 12-14% of sugar content, making it a healthy alternative to sugary carbonated drinks. Flesh colour of these watermelons are pink to red with dark brown/black seeds.', 1, 'PCS', 1, 116, 91, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000207_19-fresho-watermelon-small.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(631, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2834, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh FruitsGreen houseWatermelon KiranWatermelon - Medium (2.8 - 4 kg)NA1PCS', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Fruits', 'Green house', 'Watermelon Kiran', 'Watermelon - Medium (2.8 - 4 kg)', 'NA', 'With greenish black to smooth dark green surface, Fresho watermelons are globular in shape and are freshly picked for you directly from our farmers\r\n The juicy, sweet and grainy textured flesh is filled with 12-14% of sugar content, making it a healthy alternative to sugary carbonated drinks. Flesh colour of these watermelons are pink to red with dark brown/black seeds.', 1, 'PCS', 1, 144, 115, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40103540_4-fresho-watermelon-medium.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(632, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2835, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh VegitablesGreen houseAmerican Sweet CornExotic VegitablesNA2PCS', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Green house', 'American Sweet Corn', 'Exotic Vegitables', 'NA', 'Wrapped in lime coloured husks with silk, sweet corn contains numerous yellow succulent kernels that have a starchy and doughy consistency. The skin pops out as you bite into it.', 2, 'PCS', 2, 48, 38, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40004992_14-fresho-sweet-corn.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(633, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2836, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh VegitablesGreen houseAsh GourdAsh GourdNA250GM', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Green house', 'Ash Gourd', 'Ash Gourd', 'NA', 'Our uniformly and perfectly cut fresh ash gourds comes with a mild and soft texture.', 250, 'GM', 1, 28, 22, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40050086_3-fresho-ash-gourd-cut.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(634, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2837, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh VegitablesGreen houseBaby CornBaby CornPeeled250GM', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Green house', 'Baby Corn', 'Baby Corn', 'Peeled', 'Baby corns are small in size and handpicked before they mature.We deliver them to you fresh and peeled, so no more postponing that corn dish you wanted to make because you didn\'t get the time.', 250, 'GM', 1, 43, 34, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000017_20-fresho-baby-corn-peeled.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(635, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2838, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh VegitablesGreen houseBaby CornBaby CornUnpeeled250GM', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Green house', 'Baby Corn', 'Baby Corn', 'Unpeeled', 'A young sweet-tasting corn, baby corns are small in size and handpicked before they mature. Picking fresh and scrumptious vegetables for your healthy lifestyle is now just a click away.', 250, 'GM', 1, 19, 15, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/20000926_10-fresho-baby-corn-unpeeled.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(636, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2839, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh VegitablesGreen houseBanana StemStemNA1PCS', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Green house', 'Banana Stem', 'Stem', 'NA', 'Banana Stem is the fibrous stalk of the banana plant. It has high water content, fresh and crispy textured stalks with mild taste. Fresho stem grade bananas are offered in a pristine condition and are tasty and nutritious. We selectively pick stems of organically grown banana stem from the best farms.', 1, 'PCS', 1, 31, 25, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40036724_4-fresho-banana-stem-organically-grown.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
