(676, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2879, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh VegitablesGreen houseRaw BananaBanana - Raw GreenNA500GM', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Green house', 'Raw Banana', 'Banana - Raw Green', 'NA', 'Raw bananas are unripened bananas with a tough, green skin. Their flesh is white, dense and has a starchy-tart flavour.\r\n We selectively pick organically grown raw green bananas from the best farms.', 500, 'GM', 1, 25, 20, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000168_13-fresho-banana-raw-green.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(677, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2880, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh VegitablesGreen houseRed CapsicumCapsicum - Red, Organically GrownNA1PCS', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Green house', 'Red Capsicum', 'Capsicum - Red, Organically Grown', 'NA', 'Red capsicums are thin, smooth skinned, crunchy, mildly sweet tasting, hollow vegetables that are juicier variants of the green capsicum. They are perfect for adding a dash of colour, distinct taste and beautiful scent to your salad, pizza, pasta or even gravy preparations. They are sourced directly from farmers, so that you receive only the best quality ones which not only jazz up any dish but also offer health benefits. Product image shown is for representation purpose only, the actual product may vary based on season, produce & availability. Click here for delicious vegetable recipes - https://www.bigbasket.com/flavors/collections/227/fresh-vegetables/', 1, 'PCS', 1, 35, 28, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40124625_1-fresho-capsicum-red-organically-grown.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(678, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2881, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh VegitablesGreen houseRidge GourdRidge GourdNA1KG', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Green house', 'Ridge Gourd', 'Ridge Gourd', 'NA', 'Ridge Gourds are long vegetables with a ridged dark green skin and white spongy flesh that contains numerous seeds inside.\r\n They are rich in fiber and very prominent in Indian cooking.', 1, 'KG', 1, 74, 74, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000175_15-fresho-ridge-gourd.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(679, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2882, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh VegitablesGreen houseSambhar Onion (Small Onion)Sambhar Onion (Small Onion)NA250GM', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Green house', 'Sambhar Onion (Small Onion)', 'Sambhar Onion (Small Onion)', 'NA', 'Onion can fill your kitchen with a thick spicy aroma. It is a common base vegetable in most Indian dishes, thanks to the wonderful flavor that it adds to any dish.Also known as button onions, Sambar Onions are relatively smaller onions with a mild flavour and slightly sweet taste.', 250, 'GM', 1, 31, 20, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000178_12-fresho-sambhar-onion-small-onion.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(680, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2883, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh VegitablesGreen houseSnake GourdSnake GourdNA500GM', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Green house', 'Snake Gourd', 'Snake Gourd', 'NA', 'Snake gourds are true to their name as they have a long, curved shape with light green speckles and a waxy green skin.\r\n Their firm flesh is embedded with seeds and they taste like cucumber and have a slightly bitter taste.\r\n The fruits are orange in colour when ripe and pulpy red after complete ripening.', 500, 'GM', 1, 14, 10, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000185_11-fresho-snake-gourd.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(681, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2884, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh VegitablesGreen houseSpring OnionSpring OnionNA100GM', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Green house', 'Spring Onion', 'Spring Onion', 'NA', 'Spring onions come with a crisp texture and sweet flavor.\r\n They are moist with thin, white flesh and a green stem.\r\n The green stems are hollow, bitter, and pungent.', 100, 'GM', 1, 13, 4, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/20000981_6-fresho-spring-onion.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(682, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2885, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh VegitablesGreen houseSweet PotatoSweet PotatoNA500GM', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Green house', 'Sweet Potato', 'Sweet Potato', 'NA', 'With flesh colours ranging from white, orange and yellow, sweet potatoes are ovate and cylindrical with golden brown or white-brown skin and a delicious sweet flavour.\r\n While the white fleshed are firm, orange fleshed are softer.', 500, 'GM', 1, 30, 16, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000194_13-fresho-sweet-potato.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
(683, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2886, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh VegitablesGreen houseTender CoconutTender Coconut - MediumNA1PCS', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Green house', 'Tender Coconut', 'Tender Coconut - Medium', 'NA', 'Young, fresh and healthy tender coconuts are a pure, tasty and nutritious energy drink that keeps body hydrated round the clock.\r\n Tender coconut is the most refreshing drink and best to quench your thirst in the summer.\r\n Tender coconut has antioxidant properties which help to protect the body from free radicals.\r\n It helps to lower blood pressure level, prevent kidney stone, and support heart health.', 1, 'PCS', 1, 58, 46, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/40057966_2-fresho-tender-coconut-medium.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
