(685, 5, 'zaSBHA', 2888, 'Fruites and VegitablesFresh VegitablesGreen houseTindaTindaNA500GM', 'Vegitable and Fruits ', 'Fruites and Vegitables', 'Fresh Vegitables', 'Green house', 'Tinda', 'Tinda', 'NA', 'Tinda is a small vegetable that looks bigger than a green apple but smaller than a pumpkin.\r\n Short and squat like a pumpkin, tindas have a dark green stem and white flesh that is tender and tastes like a cucumber.\r\n The seeds within are edible.', 500, 'GM', 1, 94, 75, 'https://www.bigbasket.com/media/uploads/p/l/10000371_11-fresho-tinda.jpg', 0, '', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', '2022-01-06 00:00:00', 1, 0),
